q5uiewfrv\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '', 'Premium Wall Décor options in Dubai – for Designer Finishes  and Lasting Look
', '{"{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Looking to refresh your walls? Upgrade your interiors with our wide range of premium wall décor ideas in Dubai. We design wallpapers and Iberica sintered stone to make your walls stand out and stay stunning for years. Book a free consultation, and our team will bring ideas and samples to your home, allowing you to easily choose the right style for your space.\"}","{\"name\": \"Wallpapers:\", \"detail\": \"Wallpapers are one of the easiest ways to refresh your walls and give them a new look. They come in a wide variety of colours, patterns, and textures, making them suitable for any style of interior. They are ideal for living rooms to create a welcoming atmosphere, bedrooms for a calming backdrop, and hallways for a lively touch. Wallpapers also work wonderfully in children’s rooms, where playful designs can create a fun and inspiring environment, or in office rooms to add professionalism and style without the need for heavy renovation. We also create customised wallpapers, giving you the freedom to design walls that truly reflect your personality and preferences.\"}","{\"name\": \"Iberica Sintered Stone:\", \"detail\": \"Iberica Sintered Stone is a premium wall décor option that combines natural beauty with long-lasting durability. Known for its resistance to stains, scratches, and heat, it offers a luxurious and timeless look that remains easy to maintain for years. This material is ideal for feature walls, living rooms, offices, and high-traffic areas where both elegance and durability are essential. Its sleek and modern finish adds sophistication, making it an excellent choice for anyone looking to upgrade their interiors with a touch of luxury.\"}"}', '{}', 'Benefits of Hiring Two Guys for Wall Decor', '{"{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Two Guys in Dubai, UAE, brings expert wall décor with customised wallpapers and premium Iberica sintered stone. We provide high-quality installation and personalised service for children’s rooms, offices, or elegant living areas, making your walls truly stand out.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Free home consultation to understand your space and style needs.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Customised designing of wallpapers and wall finishes tailored to your taste.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"High-quality installation ensures smooth surfaces, perfect alignment, and long-lasting results.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Expert guidance for choosing designs that suit any room: living rooms, bedrooms, children’s rooms, or offices.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Access to premium materials, including top-quality wallpapers and Iberica sintered stone.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Attention to detail in every project to make your walls truly stand out.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"5-year warranty on all installations for peace of mind and long-term quality.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"\"}"}', '', '{"{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"\"}"}', 'Elegant Designs That Stay Beautiful', 'Recent Projects
', 'Wall Décor Success Stories: Stylish, Elegant & Built to Last', 'Give your walls the style they deserve! Two Guys has enhanced homes and offices across Dubai, UAE, with premium wall décor ideas, including designer wallpapers and Iberica sintered stone. Our wallpapers are easy to maintain, come in a wide variety of designs, and add warmth and personality to living rooms, bedrooms, children’s rooms, and office spaces. Iberica sintered stone offers durability, stain and scratch resistance, heat resistance, and a sleek, modern finish, making it perfect for feature walls, kitchens, offices, and high-traffic areas.
Every project is handled with care to match your style and taste, making your walls not just beautiful, but truly part of your home or workspace.
', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'Refresh your interiors with Two Guys in Dubai, UAE. We offer wallpapers and Iberica sintered stone with customised designs and high-quality installation.
', 'Two Guys Wall Décor | Wallpapers & Ibericaa Sintered Stone', 'The Right Wall Décor for Dubai’s Lifestyle', 'Wall Décor with Hassle-Free Installation
', ' We provide hassle-free installation for all types of wall décor – whether it’s wallpaper or Iberica Sintered Stone. Our expert team ensures every wall is perfectly styled and ready to impress.a consultation or request a quote.  ', 'Expert Setup for a Flawless Finish in Dubai, UAEin Dubai, UAE', '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
INSERT INTO public.categories (id, name, description, "createdAt", "updatedAt", "posterImageUrl", "last_editedBy", short_description, custom_url, "Banners", "BannerText", "BannerHeading", "RecallUrl", "breadCrum", "topHeading", "topDescription", "categoryHeroImages", "categoryHeroToptext", "categoryHeroHeading", "categoryHeroText", "categoryFaqs", "leftHeading", "categoryText", "Heading", paras, "bottomText", "bodyHeading", "bodyMainHeading", "bodyText", "Bannerdiscount", "salesBannerHeading", "paraText", "Bannercounter", "Canonical_Tag", "Meta_Description", "Meta_Title", "Product_Section_heading", "explore_Heading", explore_description, explore_main_heading, "seoSchema", "salesBannerImage", status) VALUES (7, 'Flooring', '', '2025-05-01 09:28:37.771', '2026-01-21 06:10:50.391', '{"imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1764324493/uploads/oei2evfgsrf99svbcx8m.webp", "public_id": "uploads/oei2evfgsrf99svbcx8m", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Admin', '', 'flooring', '{"imageUrl": "https://twoguysprod.s3.eu-north-1.amazonaws.com/1752646110551-s3", "public_id": "1752646110551-s3", "resource_type": "video"}', 'Modern Flooring Solutions for<br>Dubai Homes & Businesses', 'Flooring, Made Simple.', '', 'Flooring', 'Premium High End Flooring Options for Every Space', 'Two Guys offers a complete floor treatment service with a huge range of Floorings to match your style. Many of our options feature durable, waterproof flooring, making them a perfect choice for kitchens and busy homes in Dubai. Ready to see the quality for yourself?<a href="/book-appointment"> Book a free consultation</a> and our team will visit you with samples. Call us at <a href="tel:052 933 2833"">052 933 2833</a> to get started.', '{}', '', 'The Foundation of a Beautiful Home', '{"{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"The right floor is the foundation of a beautiful home, setting the tone for your interior. It impacts how a room feels and flows. As a leading specialist in Dubai, we provide a complete floor treatment service to help you make the perfect choice. Our collection of Floorings includes everything from the warmth of natural wood to the sleek look of modern materials. We have a style for every vision.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"The luxury floor greatly impacts your daily life. Our durable Flooring solutions are built to handle a busy family, resisting scratches and wear. We also offer beautiful water-resistance flooring that gives you peace of mind in kitchens and bathrooms, making cleanup simple. The right floor also helps create a quieter home, a great benefit for busy apartments.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Choosing from our high end flooring options is an investment in your property''s value. Our commitment goes beyond just supplying materials; our expert team ensures a perfect installation, backed by our 10+ years of experience. This guarantees your new floor looks beautiful and performs correctly for years to come. Let us help you build that perfect foundation.\"}"}', '{}', 'Sintered Stone: Upgrade the beauty of your space with sintered stone flooring that gives off the vibe of natural stone. With waterproof and scratch-resistant features, these floors stand up to heavy daily wear. We provide a comprehensive collection of sintered stones available in unique colours and textures with superior longevity.  WPC: With a perfect balance of wood and polymer, our WPC flooring offers a feel of wood with extra resilience and beauty. It is a perfect solution for kitchen flooring, basement flooring, and bathroom flooring. Explore modern and rustic designs that add a contemporary touch without compromising on strength. We at TwoGuys provide a comprehensive flooring option to elevate your space. Contact us to schedule a free consultation appointment or explore our collection online. Improve your space floor with the perfect flooring solution from TwoGuys. For a beautiful space, the first thing you should focus on is the right flooring sets. Whether you want to install a personalised floor in your cosy patio, culinary haven kitchen, or spacious garden, our premium flooring service ensures seamless installation and creates an environment that is both stylish and inviting.', '{}', '', '{}', 'Find Your Perfect Floor', 'Complete Installations', 'Explore Our Flooring Collections', '    <p>
        Our collection is selected to provide the best in design, durability, and value for your Dubai home. 
        We offer a large selection of patterns within our main flooring categories: the natural elegance of Wood, 
        the practical durability of LVT, and the luxurious strength of Sintered Stone.
    </p>

    <p><strong>SPC Flooring</strong></p>
    <p>
        SPC flooring is a modern and strong solution that gives you the beautiful look of wood or stone. 
        It''s built to be highly water-resistant and scratch-resistant, making it perfect for the busy Dubai lifestyle 
        and family homes. Its quick and perfect installation means you get a flawless finish that instantly improves your space.
    </p>

    <p><strong>Luxury Vinyl Flooring (LVT)</strong></p>
    <p>
        LVT is a practical and versatile solution, giving you the beautiful look of wood or stone. 
        As it is waterproof and durable, it''s perfect for kitchens, bathrooms, and busy family homes. 
        It also reduces noise, making it great for kids'' rooms.
    </p>

    <p><strong>Iberica Sintered Stone</strong></p>
    <p>
        For luxury and performance, Sintered Stone has the look of natural marble with unmatched strength. 
        This material is resistant to scratches, stains, and heat. Since it is waterproof and will not fade, 
        it is perfect for any room.
    </p>

    <p>
        Within each of these categories, we offer a large selection of colours, finishes, and patterns 
        to perfectly match your personal style.
    </p>', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'Discover luxury flooring in Dubai. We offer wood, LVT, and sintered stone flooring with 10+ years of expert installation. Book a free home visit.', 'Luxury Flooring Dubai | Two Guys Home Furnishings', 'Perfect for Dubai''s climate', 'Quality Materials & Expert Guidance', 'Want to see our collection in your own home? Book your free consultation today. We bring the samples', 'Dubai''s Choice for Premium Flooring Solutions', '', '[{"imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747133286/uploads/c3b3ibwep43ivmug6w4i.png", "public_id": "uploads/c3b3ibwep43ivmug6w4i", "resource_type": "image"}]', 'PUBLISHED');
INSERT INTO public.categories (id, name, description, "createdAt", "updatedAt", "posterImageUrl", "last_editedBy", short_description, custom_url, "Banners", "BannerText", "BannerHeading", "RecallUrl", "breadCrum", "topHeading", "topDescription", "categoryHeroImages", "categoryHeroToptext", "categoryHeroHeading", "categoryHeroText", "categoryFaqs", "leftHeading", "categoryText", "Heading", paras, "bottomText", "bodyHeading", "bodyMainHeading", "bodyText", "Bannerdiscount", "salesBannerHeading", "paraText", "Bannercounter", "Canonical_Tag", "Meta_Description", "Meta_Title", "Product_Section_heading", "explore_Heading", explore_description, explore_main_heading, "seoSchema", "salesBannerImage", status) VALUES (17, 'Carpet', '', '2025-11-14 09:48:57.209', '2025-12-15 10:44:56.891', '{"imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1764583499/uploads/ta9dgr2l77ntn94rrbl5.webp", "public_id": "uploads/ta9dgr2l77ntn94rrbl5", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Admin', NULL, 'carpets-and-rugs', '{"imageUrl": "https://twoguysprod.s3.eu-north-1.amazonaws.com/1764583554409-s3", "public_id": "1764583554409-s3", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Design your interior with our<br> premium carpet collection.', 'Luxury You Can Feel in Every Step', NULL, 'Carpet', '', NULL, '{"{\"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1764583530/uploads/zjqkre1xhwuwqkp4kuzo.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/zjqkre1xhwuwqkp4kuzo\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '', 'Style your Dubai villa beautifully from floor to finish.
', '{"{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Make your home look and feel amazing with our luxurious carpet collection at Two Guys Home Furnishings. We have a wide range of colours, patterns, and textures, from soft greys and light neutrals to bright, bold shades that can change the whole look of your room.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Each carpet is made from quality materials like wool, polyester, and blended fibers, so they are soft underfoot, durable, and easy to clean.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our collection works in any room: living rooms, bedrooms, hallways, or even offices. You can use our carpets to add a little comfort, cover floors, or simply make a space feel more welcoming. They don’t just cover your floor; they bring life to your rooms, highlight your furniture, and create a cosy feeling that everyone will enjoy.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"With so many designs and sizes to choose from, you can mix and match to find the perfect carpet for every room in your home. From soft hallway runners to large living room carpets, each one is crafted to last while keeping your space stylish, comfortable, and welcoming.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', '', '{}', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', NULL, '', 'Discover a wide range of carpets in Dubai. Choose from various colours, textures, and sizes for living rooms, bedrooms, hallways, and offices. 
', 'Premium Carpets in Dubai | Two Guys Home Furnishings', 'Carpet & Rugs', '', 'Explore our wide range of carpets in different colours, textures, and sizes. Enjoy a free home consultation and a 5-year warranty for complete confidence in your choice.
Call +971 50 597 4495 to get the perfect carpet for your home today!
', 'Fast & Expert Carpet Service
 Dubai’s Trusted Choice
', '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
INSERT INTO public.categories (id, name, description, "createdAt", "updatedAt", "posterImageUrl", "last_editedBy", short_description, custom_url, "Banners", "BannerText", "BannerHeading", "RecallUrl", "breadCrum", "topHeading", "topDescription", "categoryHeroImages", "categoryHeroToptext", "categoryHeroHeading", "categoryHeroText", "categoryFaqs", "leftHeading", "categoryText", "Heading", paras, "bottomText", "bodyHeading", "bodyMainHeading", "bodyText", "Bannerdiscount", "salesBannerHeading", "paraText", "Bannercounter", "Canonical_Tag", "Meta_Description", "Meta_Title", "Product_Section_heading", "explore_Heading", explore_description, explore_main_heading, "seoSchema", "salesBannerImage", status) VALUES (4, 'Window Coverings', '', '2025-04-24 10:53:48.986', '2026-01-14 12:00:00.39', '{"imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1764324458/uploads/up9xlkst9k9wjrmnfv8m.webp", "public_id": "uploads/up9xlkst9k9wjrmnfv8m", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Admin', '', 'window-coverings', '{"imageUrl": "https://twoguysprod.s3.eu-north-1.amazonaws.com/1750157942079-s3", "public_id": "1750157942079-s3", "resource_type": "video"}', 'Blinds, Curtains & Shutters – Crafted for<br>Every Window, Designed for Every Lifestyle', 'Two Guys Window Coverings', '', 'Window Covering', '', '', '{"{\"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1764567735/uploads/a9urhlmvvqpzm1as2w3s.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/a9urhlmvvqpzm1as2w3s\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1764567738/uploads/mwthl4ixszgpb0sc8pm7.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/mwthl4ixszgpb0sc8pm7\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1764567742/uploads/m0l20yhfympzssxmuvu6.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/m0l20yhfympzssxmuvu6\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '', 'Custom Blinds, Curtains, and Shutters
', '{"{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Are your windows letting in too much sunlight, heat, or unwanted attention? Window coverings solve these problems while adding style, comfort, and privacy to your home. At Two Guys, we offer a wide range of options to meet every need, and they are available in both manual and motorised styles. You can select from a variety of blinds, including blackout, sunscreen, and day & night options; curtains in blackout, sheer, and layered designs; and shutters such as full height, plantation, solid panel, and café-style or special-shaped options. With 10+ years of experience, 18,000+ happy customers, and a 5-year warranty, we make your windows functional, stylish, and comfortable. We at Two Guys have the following types of window coverings.\"}"}', '{"{\"name\": \"Blinds\", \"detail\": \"Blinds are available in aluminium, PVC, wood, or soft fabrics. Aluminium and PVC blinds are lightweight, easy to clean, and ideal for kitchens, bathrooms, or offices. Wooden blinds add warmth and elegance, making them perfect for living rooms, bedrooms, or lounges. Roman blinds are most suited for bedrooms and living areas. \"}","{\"name\": \"Curtains\", \"detail\": \"Curtains are available in a variety of fabrics, including cotton, linen, velvet, and polyester. Cotton and linen offer a soft, natural feel, which is great for bedrooms or living areas. Velvet brings a rich, luxurious look, perfect for lounges or formal spaces. Polyester is durable, low-maintenance, and suitable for high-traffic rooms.\"}","{\"name\": \"Shutters\", \"detail\": \"Shutters are crafted from MDF, Paulownia, or Basswood. MDF is practical and smooth, suitable for hallways, offices, or everyday use. Paulownia is lightweight, resistant to sunlight, and ideal for large or upper-floor windows. Basswood is a strong and elegant choice, perfect for feature windows, bedrooms, or living areas where style and durability are paramount.  MDF is the most cost-effective, Paulownia sits in the middle, and Basswood is our premium wood.  Choosing the right material ensures your window coverings provide privacy, insulation, and long-lasting performance while enhancing the beauty of every room.\"}"}', '', '{}', '', '{}', '', 'Recent Installations', 'Your One-Stop Solution for Window Coverings in Dubai', 'A family in Dubai recently trusted us with their home’s windows. We provided free consultation, precise measurements, custom manufacturing, and professional installation for their window coverings. Seeing each room come to life with perfect light, privacy, and style reminded us why we love delivering window coverings that truly fit every space.
', '', '', '', '2025-07-23 00:00:00', '', 'Discover custom blinds, curtains, and shutters in Dubai. Two Guys offers free consultation and expert installation for every home style.
', 'Window Coverings in Dubai | Two Guys Home Furnishings', '', 'Fast & Professional Window Covering Solutions
', 'At Two Guys, we design and install custom window coverings that bring both beauty and functionality to your home. From elegant curtains to sleek blinds and timeless shutters, every product is designed to fit your space perfectly.<br>
Call us today at <a href="tel: +971 50 597 4495">+971 50 597 4495</a> to transform your windows with stylish, durable, and perfectly fitted coverings by Two Guys.', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Blinds, Curtains & Shutters', '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');


