', '{"{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"At our production house, we design a wide range of window shutters, including Full Height, Bay Window, Tier-on-Tier, Café Style, Solid Panel, Tracked System, and Special Shape Shutters. All of these are custom-made, and the material you choose depends on the style and area of the window.  You can pick MDF for compact areas,  lightweight Paulownia for medium-sized windows, and for a premium appearance, our Basswood shutter is the best option; it is durable, elegant, and perfect for larger windows. Each material is carefully selected to ensure your shutters look beautiful, fit perfectly, and last for years to come.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Each shutter adds timeless elegance, controls light and privacy, and gives your interiors a luxurious finish. Our window shutters come with a 5-year warranty and require 6-8 weeks for installation. They are designed to last, making them perfect for Dubai homes that prioritise both beauty and durability.\"}"}', '{}', 'Stylish Shutters for Every Window', 'Made to fit, built to last.', '{"{\"name\": \"Made-to-Measure Shutters for Every Space\", \"detail\": \"At Two Guys, we create custom shutters that fit every part of your home perfectly. Each style is designed for comfort, privacy, and a clean, elegant look. Here’s where you can use them:\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"<ul> <li><b>Kitchen Window Shutters:</b>  Handle heat well, and keep your kitchen bright.</li> <li><b>Indoor shutters:</b> Add a timeless touch to living rooms and bedrooms.</li> <li><b>Bathroom Window Shutters:</b> Moisture-resistant, keep your bathroom fresh and neat.</li> <li><b>Basswood Window Shutters:</b> Strong and modern, perfect for outdoor or high-exposure spaces.</li> </ul>\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Every shutter is made to measure to fit your windows just right.\"}","{\"name\": \"From Consultation to Installation – We Handle It All\", \"detail\": \"At Two Guys, we make the process of getting new shutters easy from start to finish. We begin with a free home consultation where we take accurate measurements to ensure a perfect fit. Your shutters are crafted from high-quality materials. Our experts then handle the installation with care. From consultation to installation, we ensure a smooth and stress-free experience, allowing you to enjoy beautiful shutters that last for years.\"}"}', '{}', '{"{\"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1764828155/uploads/c0qrr7qcqbsqe3walzmk.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/c0qrr7qcqbsqe3walzmk\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '{"{\"name\": \"Custom-Made Louvered Shutters for Your Home\", \"detail\": \"In made-to-measure shutters Louvers are the small, adjustable slats that let you control sunlight and privacy. You can tilt them open to let in light or close them for a calm, private feel. At Two Guys, our custom-made louvered shutters are designed to fit your windows perfectly. Whether you love the classic look of wooden shutters or want something modern and sleek, we’ll help you find the right style for your home. \"}","{\"name\": \"Why Choose Two Guys for Shutters in Dubai?\", \"detail\": \"Hiring us comes with lots of perks. We’ve been installing shutters in Dubai homes and offices for a while now, so we have plenty of experience. At Two Guys, we offer top-notch handcrafted wooden shutters, have a talented and experienced team, and ensure everything fits perfectly. Without wasting any time, visit our showroom located in Al Quoz, Dubai or call us at <a href=\\\"tel:052 933 2833\\\">052 933 2833</a> and also fill out the online contact form  to get a free, non-obligation quotation as soon as possible.  Perfect for Dubai''s \"}"}', '{}', '', '', 'Our Recent Installation', 'Hassle-Free, Beautiful, and Built to Last', 'We’ve just completed another beautiful window shutter installation! The space now looks brighter, stylish, and more comfortable. At Two Guys, we’ve proudly served over 18,000 happy customers with easy, hassle-free installation and lasting quality, making every home look its best, one window at a time.', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Shutters Installation', 'Our team offers customised window coverings across Dubai with a 05-year installation warranty. <br>Book a free consultation today and give your windows the upgrade they deserve!', NULL, '', 'Discover plantation shutters made to fit your windows perfectly. Premium materials, expert installation, and timeless elegance for Dubai homes.
', ' Plantation Shutters Dubai | Custom-Made by Two Guys', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
