', '{"{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"For a look of modern luxury without the cost and mess, Two Guys Home Furnishings offers a full range of architectural vinyl wrap surfaces. This gives you the beautiful look of real wood, marble, leather or metal with incredible versatility. It is engineered to be highly durable, easy to clean, water resistant, and scratch-resistant. Its high-quality materials will not peel or fade, making it a perfect, long-lasting choice for updating homes and offices in the busy Dubai climate.</br>When it comes to application, precision is key. Our expert team ensures every surface is wrapped perfectly. The result is a flawless, bubble-free finish that instantly transforms your space.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our vinyl film wrap solution includes four key points:\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"<b>1. The Vinyl Film:</b> A durable, multi-layered material designed for longevity.</br><b>2.  Finish Options:</b> Choose from hundreds of styles, from realistic wood and marble to solid colours and metallics. </br><b>3. Professional Application:</b> Our expert team guarantees a flawless, bubble-free finish on any surface.</br><b>4. Adhesive Technology:</b> We use high-quality self-adhesive vinyl film for a strong, lasting bond.\"}"}', '{}', '', '', '{}', '{}', '{}', '{}', '{}', '', '', '', '', '', 'A Flawless Finish, Guaranteed', 'Dubai''s Experts in Architectural Vinyl Wraps', 'Contact our expert team for a free consultation and explore our stunning collection.', NULL, '', 'Get the luxury look of marble or wood for less. At Two Guys, we offer fast, affordable vinyl film wrap services for most surfaces in your Dubai home.', 'Vinyl Film Wrap Dubai | Kitchen, Walls & Furniture Wrapping', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
