, this is the perfect choice for inside your home or as outdoor floor tiles in the Dubai heat.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"When it comes to installation, precision is key. Our expert team ensures every slab fits perfectly. The result is a flawless finish that instantly improves your space, ready to impress from day one.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our Sintered Stone flooring solution includes four key points:\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \" <b>1. The Stone Slabs: </b>Available in oversized formats for a clean look with minimal joints.<br> <b>2. Finish Options: </b>Choose from many styles to match your interior, including classic polished stone floor tiles or bold black stone floor tiles.<br><b>3. Professional Installation: </b> Our expert team guarantees a flawless and perfectly level finish.<br><b>4. Grout & Edging: </b>We use high-quality materials for all finishing touches to ensure lasting results.\"}"}', '{}', 'Collection', 'Our Bestselling Sintered Stone Surfaces', '{}', '{}', '{}', '{}', '{}', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Dubai''s Choice for Premium Flooring Solutions', 'Book a free consultation to see our Sintered Stone samples, including options for black stone floor tiles.', '{"imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1748948446/uploads/tzf3ssebxu1ihcjoxpc1.webp", "public_id": "uploads/tzf3ssebxu1ihcjoxpc1", "resource_type": "image"}', '', 'Shop luxury Sintered Stone flooring in Dubai. The perfect, durable surface for indoor floors, walls, and even outdoor tiles. Book a free consultation.
', 'Ibérica Sintered Stone Flooring | Two Guys Home Furnishings', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
INSERT INTO public."subCategories" (id, name, description, "createdAt", "updatedAt", "posterImageUrl", "last_editedBy", short_description, custom_url, "categoryId", "Banners", "BannerText", "BannerHeading", "leftHeading", "categoryText", "categoryHeroImages", "categoryHeroToptext", "categoryHeroHeading", "categoryHeroText", "categoryFaqs", "collectionHeading", "collectionMainHeading", "QualityHeadings", "QualityText", "QualityImages", "CustomHeading", "CustomText", "Product_Section_heading", "bottomText", "bodyHeading", "bodyMainHeading", "bodyText", "explore_Heading", explore_main_heading, explore_description, "professionalServiceImage", "Canonical_Tag", "Meta_Description", "Meta_Title", "breadCrum", "seoSchema", status) VALUES (2, 'Blinds', '', '2025-05-03 04:53:11.627', '2026-01-12 09:31:51.851', '{"imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1764401761/uploads/excet1gbso6yfir4wkl2.webp", "public_id": "uploads/excet1gbso6yfir4wkl2", "resource_type": "image"}', NULL, '', 'blinds', 4, '{"imageUrl": "https://twoguysprod.s3.eu-north-1.amazonaws.com/1752321217247-s3", "public_id": "1752321217247-s3", "resource_type": "video"}', 'Custom-Made Blinds </br>In Dubai, UAE ', 'Two Guys Custom Blinds', 'Blind Installation Service: Made-To-Measure Blackout and Motorised Blinds For Your Windows', '{"{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Why settle for the basics when you can have extraordinary?\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"At Two Guys, we bring you the future of window coverings. We have solutions for every window, regardless of its size and shape. We start by measuring, then move on to manufacturing, and finally install them. With a team of 50 dedicated staff, we ensure everything goes smoothly from start to finish.\"}"}', '{"{\"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1746263727/uploads/adp9ldn1nejtfwvktreh.jpg\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/adp9ldn1nejtfwvktreh\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1746263703/uploads/vza0latgelty5dyikjjd.png\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/vza0latgelty5dyikjjd\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1746263705/uploads/zrds69myeo6laxy9mbzq.png\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/zrds69myeo6laxy9mbzq\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', 'Blinds That Are Made for You', 'Types of Window Blinds We Offer: ', '{"{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"A custom-made window blind can completely change the look and feel of a space, whether it’s a home, office, or commercial area. Here are some of our most popular choices to suit different needs and styles.\"}"}', '{"{\"name\": \"Roller Window Blinds\", \"detail\": \"Our roller blinds offer high-quality blinds, whether you need blackout blinds for complete darkness and insulation or sunscreen blinds to filter harsh sunlight. Our blinds keep your space cool. Window blinds in Dubai are specifically designed to suit the local climate, helping protect interiors from UV damage, reducing heat, and enhancing overall comfort.\"}","{\"name\": \"Custom Vertical Blinds \", \"detail\": \"Our vertical blinds are perfect for large windows and sliding doors. They offer easy light control with tilting slats for adjustable brightness and full privacy when closed. Our blinds for windows are designed for a sleek look; they neatly stack to the side when open. \"}","{\"name\": \"Luxury Roman Blinds\", \"detail\": \"At Two Guys, we create custom-made Roman blinds designed for your space, no off-the-shelf options, just a perfect fit. With a wide range of fabrics, textures, and patterns, they complement any style, whether it''s office blinds for windows or blinds for bedroom windows. Our window blinds in the UAE are designed to sit neatly, like roller blinds, all in one perfect blind.\"}"}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Highest Quality Fabric Blinds Shop in Dubai \", \"detail\": \"\"}"}', '{"{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"At Two Guys, we believe good blinds start with good fabric. That’s why we use only high-quality materials from trusted designers. Every fabric and installation comes with a 5-year warranty, so you can feel confident in what you choose.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our team listens to your needs and works with you to create made-to-measure blinds that fit your space and style. Whether it’s for your home or office, we make the whole process easy, smooth, and customised just for you.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our showroom in Al Quoz, Dubai, is the perfect place to explore our collection in person. If you prefer, we also offer free home visits, where our experts bring fabric samples to help you make the best choice. We’re not just about selling blinds; we’re about delivering excellence with every installation. Let us help you create the perfect window covering for your space.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Visit our showroom or <a href=\\\"/book-appointment/\\\">book a free consultation</a> today!\"}"}', '{"{\"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1746263796/uploads/ndyscmagwtlqujf67mox.jpg\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/ndyscmagwtlqujf67mox\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '{}', '{}', '', '', 'Recent installations', ' Expertly Installed Window Blinds: Crafted to Perfection', 'We take pride in delivering high-quality custom blinds. Our latest projects showcase expertly installed roller blinds, Roman blinds, vertical blinds, motorised blinds, honeycomb blinds, sunscreen or blackout roller blinds, and day and night blinds, all designed to complement diverse interiors. From smart city apartments to luxurious villas, we guarantee a precise installation and premium finishes. ', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Blinds Installation', 'Our team offers customised window coverings across Dubai with a 5-year installation warranty.<br>Book a free consultation today and give your windows the upgrade they deserve!', '{"altText": "wer", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1746439524/uploads/c9ty6pqh7m48s2hzclg2.jpg", "public_id": "uploads/c9ty6pqh7m48s2hzclg2", "resource_type": "image"}', '', 'Get custom-made blinds in Dubai. Choose from roller, Roman and vertical blinds with 1-2 day installation and a 5-year warranty. 
', 'Custom Window Blinds in Dubai |  1-2 day Installation', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
INSERT INTO public."subCategories" (id, name, description, "createdAt", "updatedAt", "posterImageUrl", "last_editedBy", short_description, custom_url, "categoryId", "Banners", "BannerText", "BannerHeading", "leftHeading", "categoryText", "categoryHeroImages", "categoryHeroToptext", "categoryHeroHeading", "categoryHeroText", "categoryFaqs", "collectionHeading", "collectionMainHeading", "QualityHeadings", "QualityText", "QualityImages", "CustomHeading", "CustomText", "Product_Section_heading", "bottomText", "bodyHeading", "bodyMainHeading", "bodyText", "explore_Heading", explore_main_heading, explore_description, "professionalServiceImage", "Canonical_Tag", "Meta_Description", "Meta_Title", "breadCrum", "seoSchema", status) VALUES (3, 'Curtains', '', '2025-05-03 09:23:45.418', '2025-12-12 10:57:30.533', '{"altText": "CurtainsCurtains", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1746764781/uploads/iqlbvo4hkbpjegjyduwq.jpg", "public_id": "uploads/iqlbvo4hkbpjegjyduwq", "resource_type": "image"}', NULL, '', 'curtains', 4, '{"imageUrl": "https://twoguysprod.s3.eu-north-1.amazonaws.com/1749897268730-s3", "public_id": "1749897268730-s3", "resource_type": "video"}', 'Made To Measure Curtains,<br>Thousands of Fabric Options,<br>Installed in 2-3 Days!', ' Custom-Made Curtains', 'curtains Installation Service: Window Blinds, Blackout Blinds and Motorised Blinds', '{}', '{"{\"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1746264044/uploads/m42oqqobuwpiwzsisnpf.jpg\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/m42oqqobuwpiwzsisnpf\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1746264028/uploads/ntryfzdseg54in097d79.png\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/ntryfzdseg54in097d79\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1746264029/uploads/ycfwvaomiwo3hi1u8ogp.png\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/ycfwvaomiwo3hi1u8ogp\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '', 'Highest Standards, Custom-Made Curtains', '{"{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our business started making exceptional curtains in 2014, and we’re very proud to still be making curtains for windows today, thanks to our dedicated team of 50+ staff. With an incredible selection of fabrics, our made-to-measure curtain service creates high-quality curtains exactly to your specifications.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Whether you are looking for blackout curtains, pencil pleat curtains, or linen curtains, we will create the perfect pair for your space. Our curtains add sophistication, privacy and protection from light and noise, and become a stunning focal point in any room.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Having bespoke curtains made for your home couldn’t be easier. Start by booking a free consultation, and our team will bring samples so you can find the perfect fabric for your windows. We will take care of measuring your new made-to-measure curtains and even helping you select the perfect.\"}"}', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Don''t Make It Fit, Have It Made To Fit!\", \"detail\": \"\"}"}', '{"{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"At Two Guys Home Furnishings, we understand that every home is different, and so is every home-owner. That’s why our made-to-measure curtains collection is designed to give you exactly what you need—nothing more, nothing less. When it comes to fabric, we don’t believe in limitations.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"We test all of our fabrics before we put them in our collections. You''ll find a selection of textures and finishes, from soft, sheer veils that let in just the right amount of light to rich, warm velvets that add richness and depth. Our textured plains add quiet elegance without overpowering a space, while patterns help to create a bold look.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"But fabric alone isn’t enough. We have blackout fabrics or we can add blackout lining to regular fabrics, so your curtains aren''t just beautiful but also functional. Blocking harsh sunlight, regulating temperature, and creating the right vibe all year round is what we aim for. Because no two windows are the same, we offer different heading options, like pencil pleats, eyelets or s-wave (ripplefold curtains), so your curtains don''t just fit-they feel like they were meant to be there.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Also, we are so passionate about customisation - we let you pick the fabric, the lining, the heading width, and the length to make it exactly how you need it. Unlike ready-made curtains.\"}"}', '{"{\"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1746264083/uploads/h473xjdxgcrohv6mddz5.jpg\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/h473xjdxgcrohv6mddz5\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '{}', '{}', '', '', 'Recent installations', 'We''re Trusted For Expert Installations', 'Our customers love us not just for the quality of our curtains, but for the care and expertise we bring to every step. Whether it’s helping you choose the right fabric, guiding you through measurements, or ensuring a flawless installation, we treat every home like it’s our own. We don’t believe in the hard-sell technique.', '', 'Trusted Choice for Customised Window Blinds & Curtains In Dubai', 'Regardless of the size and scale of the project, we measure, make and install outstanding window curtains for every single project.', NULL, 'testcurtains', 'Explore high-quality curtains in Dubai with premium fabrics, blackout options, and expert installation for a seamless experience.', 'Made-to-Measure Curtains Dubai | Curtains & Installation', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
