', '{"{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"For a floor that combines the beautiful look of natural materials with modern performance, choose LVT flooring from Two Guys Home Furnishings. This luxury vinyl flooring uses high-definition imaging to perfectly capture the texture of real wood or stone. It is designed to be water resistant, scratch-resistant, and incredibly durable, making it a perfect fit for the busy Dubai lifestyle.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"When it comes to installation, our expert team ensures a flawless result. The final finish is a stunning and practical floor that is ready for your family''s daily life from the moment we are done.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our LVT flooring Dubai solution includes four key points:\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"<b>1. The Design Layer: </b>High-definition visuals that realistically mimic wood or stone.<br><b>2. The Protective Wear Layer: </b>A tough top layer that resists scratches, stains, and scuffs.<br><b>3. Professional Installation: </b> Our expert team ensures every tile or plank is fitted perfectly.<br><b>4. Comfort & Sound Reduction: </b>LVT is softer underfoot and quieter to walk on than many other hard floors.\"}"}', '{}', 'Collection', 'Our Bestselling LVT Flooring Dubai Designs', '{}', '{}', '{}', '{}', '{}', '', '', '', '', '', '', 'Dubai''s Choice for Luxury Vinyl Flooring', 'Book a free consultation to see our LVT flooring samples, including our popular wood and stone effects.', NULL, '', 'Shop luxury vinyl flooring in Dubai. Our LVT flooring is water resistant, scratch-resistant, and realistically mimics the look of wood and stone.
', 'LVT Flooring Dubai | Stylish & Durable Vinyl Floors', NULL, NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
