blic_id\": \"uploads/u2kjdbselpycm28bfrah\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Bedroom Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747735000/uploads/dgkysybkg976uxbyg9xk.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/dgkysybkg976uxbyg9xk\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Bedroom Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747735001/uploads/eivpgenwpcislahu62mc.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/eivpgenwpcislahu62mc\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-07 08:00:46.963', '2025-12-02 11:36:56.151', '', 'Choose from thousands of high-quality fabrics for privacy, light control, and a cozy atmosphere. Expert measuring and installation included.', 'Bedroom Curtains | Blackout, Sheer & Custom Made-to-Measure', NULL, 'bedroom-curtains', 'Bedroom Curtains', '{"altText": "Bedroom Curtains", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747734976/uploads/cl1y7z3zpth0iwnafyxq.webp", "public_id": "uploads/cl1y7z3zpth0iwnafyxq", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Custom Bedroom Curtains –<br>Made-to-Measure for Comfort & Style', 'Custom curtains, pure comfort', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Bedroom Curtains\", \"detail\": \"Curtains in a bedroom should never be an afterthought. They are one of the first things you see in the morning and the last thing you close at night. At Two Guys Home Furnishings, we believe that choosing the right bedroom curtains isn’t about trends—it’s about how you live, how you sleep, and how you want your space to feel. Whether you want soft, flowing sheers, complete blackout, or a combination that shifts with your day, we help you find the perfect bedroom window curtains.\"}","{\"name\": \"Expert Guidance, High-Quality Materials, And A Team That Genuinely Cares\", \"detail\": \"We offer thousands of fabric choices, from natural linens and rich velvets to light-filtering sheers and bedroom blackout curtains. But having options isn’t enough—it’s about finding the right one for you. That’s why our team takes the time to listen, advise, and guide you through the process. Whether you need a specific fabric for better sleep, a certain color to match your interior, or a custom length to fit floor-to-ceiling windows, we help you make decisions that work for your space—not just push a sale.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Quality matters, and we don’t cut corners. Each room curtain is carefully made using high-quality fabrics that drape beautifully and last for years, without fading or losing their shape. We don’t believe in rushing through orders just to move on to the next job. Every detail, from the stitching, lining to bedroom curtain design is handled with precision, ensuring that your curtains look and function perfectly from day one. You can check our recent installation projects for more bedroom curtain ideas.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Bedroom Curtains', 'Luxe movement', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Book your free consultation today and experience the future of smart living', 'Handcrafted by artisans with a passion for creativity, Two Guys Home Furnishings help bring your imagination to reality with their best home decor services and products.', 'null', 4, 3, '', 70, 'PUBLISHED');
