424/uploads/x5u5ydzetg3hvq3rhshw.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/x5u5ydzetg3hvq3rhshw\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Full Height Shutters\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747806425/uploads/mmlnkrte5lgmjphd7b2w.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/mmlnkrte5lgmjphd7b2w\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Full Height Shutters\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747806427/uploads/axuwou5wzj01942fjjfx.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/axuwou5wzj01942fjjfx\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-07 09:22:06.952', '2025-12-02 05:54:25.277', '', 'Our Full Height Shutters provide complete floor-to-ceiling coverage for tall windows. Get superior light control, full privacy, and striking style. ', 'Full Height Shutters: Floor-to-Ceiling | Total Coverage', NULL, 'full-height-shutters', 'Full Height Shutters', '{"altText": "Full Height Shutters", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747806398/uploads/on2uimf8eqr0zk1totta.webp", "public_id": "uploads/on2uimf8eqr0zk1totta", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Full Height Shutters: Floor-to-Ceiling</br> Shutters Designed for Modern Living', 'Total Coverage, Total Control', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Full Length Shutters: Modern Style Framed in Every Panel\", \"detail\": \"These full length shutters run from floor to ceiling in one smooth panel, giving you complete privacy, superior light management, and a striking architectural feature all in one. Unlike smaller shutters or basic blinds, full height designs cover your entire window opening without breaks or gaps. This makes them perfect for tall windows, patio doors, and large glass panels where you need both function and visual impact. \"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"They work beautifully in living areas, master bedrooms, and any space with oversized windows that deserve special attention. Their continuous vertical lines create a sense of height and elegance that other window coverings simply can''t match. For a look of modern minimalism or timeless sophistication, these full height shutters adapt to your vision while giving you full control over sunlight, airflow, and privacy with just a tilt of the louvres.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Every investment in our full height window shutters from Two Guys Home Furnishings is protected by a comprehensive 5-year warranty. From the moment you order, you can expect installation to be completed efficiently within 6–8 weeks.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Full Height Shutters', 'Explore Our Materials, Colours, and Full-Length Design Options', 'Quick & Reliable Service', 'Your Full Height Shutter Experts Are Here', 'Need advice on materials, measurements, or choosing the perfect style for your space? Don''t worry. Our specialists offer quick and reliable service and are ready to guide you. We''ll walk you through all the full height shutter options.', 'null', 4, 4, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
