', 'Custom Wooden Venetian Blinds – Free Fitting | At Two Guys', NULL, 'wood-venetian-blinds', 'Wooden Venetian Blinds', '{"altText": "Wooden Blinds", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749806880/uploads/hehj9l7f4rep1zv7rijf.webp", "public_id": "uploads/hehj9l7f4rep1zv7rijf", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Custom Wooden Venetian Blinds: </br>Timeless Elegance & Lasting Quality', 'Your Comfort, Your Blinds', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Wooden Venetian Blinds\", \"detail\": \"Wood Venetian blinds are a type of window covering made from horizontal wooden slats that can be tilted, raised, or lowered to control light, privacy, and airflow. Wooden Venetian blinds give any room a feeling of sophistication and organic charm. We offer the ideal shade to match your décor, whether you want a rich walnut tone or a light oak finish.\"}","{\"name\": \"Wooden Venetian Blinds: Free Installation & Perfect Fit\", \"detail\": \"To provide privacy and comfort, our Wooden Venetian Blinds are made with easy-to-adjust wooden slats that let in the ideal amount of sunshine. They are a wise long-term investment because they are long-lasting, stylish, and made of the highest-quality wood. Whether it’s for a large window, sliding door, or bay window, we offer a wide selection to suit your needs. Our wood Venetian blinds, also present in the form of motorised blinds, are perfect for large windows or hard-to-reach areas. We provide free measurement, selection, fitting, and quotations to assist you in finding the perfect fit of Venetian blinds for your space. \"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our mission at Two Guys is to provide outstanding service and hassle-free installation. Our experts help you select the best patterns, finishes, and maintenance choices so that your Venetian blinds for windows will look gorgeous and perform well for many years to come. We take pride in leaving your place spotless and collaborating with you to review the final result to ensure your complete satisfaction.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"<b>Book your free in-home visit today and experience wooden Venetian blinds, designed just for you.</b></br>Visit our showroom or book a free consultation today!\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Wood Venetian Blinds', 'Classic Design for every Window', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Blinds Installation', 'Our team offers customised window coverings across Dubai, backed by a 5-year installation warranty.<br>Book a free consultation today and give your windows the upgrade they deserve!', 'null', 4, 2, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
