', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Motorised Blinds, Designed for You\", \"detail\": \"Motorised blinds, or automated blinds, are window blinds that you can open and close by using a remote control, smartphone app, or even voice command—you can operate them automatically instead of pulling cords or chains by hand. Just integrate your blinds with the Somfy Smart Hub app or your smart home system, and use Google Assistant or Alexa for smart control.\"}","{\"name\": \"Custom-Fit Motorised Blinds with Smart Operating System\", \"detail\": \"Hands full in the kitchen? Just say, ''Alexa, open the blinds,'' and let automation brighten your space. At Two Guys Home Furnishings, your home automation blinds are designed for modern living. These blinds eliminate the hassle of manual operation, allowing you to control them effortlessly with a remote control or wall switch. Whether you have hard-to-reach windows or multiple blinds in a room, automation ensures a smooth and effortless experience. Plus, with a cord-free design, they’re a safer choice for homes with children and pets.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Want to take blind automation a step further? Add the Somfy Smart Hub to control your blinds from anywhere using an app. You can also integrate them with Alexa, Google Assistant, or your smart home system, allowing hands-free voice control.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Set schedules to maximise natural light, save energy, and enhance security by programming your blinds to open and close at specific times—even when you''re away. At the core of our service are quality, precision, and customer satisfaction. We’ve earned the trust of customers, with 750+ 5-star reviews backing our commitment to excellence.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"<b>Book your free consultation today and experience the future of smart living</b>\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Motorised Blinds', ' A Smart Solution for a Peaceful Home', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Blinds Installation', 'Our team offers customised window coverings across Dubai with a 5-year installation warranty.<br>Book a free consultation today and give your windows the upgrade they deserve!', 'null', 4, 2, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
