\": \"uploads/khbjzk3hsmwipaplxktv\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Blackout Blinds\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749723187/uploads/hddvdcplpyr2dd8qvvwt.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/hddvdcplpyr2dd8qvvwt\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Blackout Blinds\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749723188/uploads/wtaug1qvhcha5ebsnizp.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/wtaug1qvhcha5ebsnizp\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-07 07:37:34.313', '2025-12-01 11:20:13.871', '', 'Get blackout blinds in Dubai, available in roller, Roman, and thermal pleated styles with 0% transparency. Free installation with a 5-year warranty. ', 'Custom Blackout Blinds in Dubai | Free Installation', NULL, 'blackout-blinds', 'Blackout Blinds', '{"altText": "Blackout Blinds", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749723145/uploads/knxseyaig8tshe2xnfyk.webp", "public_id": "uploads/knxseyaig8tshe2xnfyk", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Custom Blackout Blinds in Dubai –</br> Total Darkness, Total Comfort', 'Your View, Your Blind', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Customised Blackout Blinds\", \"detail\": \"Blackout blinds are specifically made to block outside light, with overall darkness, privacy, and insulation. These blinds are made from high-quality blackout materials and are perfect for home theaters, offices, nurseries, and bedrooms because they properly block out heat, light, and reduce undesirable noises. \"}","{\"name\": \"Blackout Blinds: Made-to-Measure Comfort with Free Installation\", \"detail\": \"At Two Guys, we have a wide range of blackout blinds in a huge range of colours, from contemporary to classic and made to measure to perfectly fit your windows. Whether you choose classic roller blinds, luxurious Roman blinds, or thermal pleated blinds with blackout lining, you’ll enjoy better light control and extra insulation, and a darker, more peaceful space. With their extra-opaque lining, these made-to-measure blackout blinds give the highest level of privacy, so you don''t have to worry about creating shadows at night or about outsiders being able to see into your house. For people who work night shifts, a blackout roller blind is also a lifesaver because it blocks out as much light from the outside as possible, guaranteeing a restful night''s sleep during the day.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our blackout blinds not only provide 0% transparency for complete privacy but also help reduce energy costs by maintaining indoor temperature. Every set comes with a 5-year warranty on chains and mechanisms and on the fabric, which has a long-lasting quality for your home.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Visit our showroom or book a free consultation today!\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Blackout Blinds', 'Total Control Over Light', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Blinds Installation', 'Our team offers customised window coverings across Dubai with a 5-year installation warranty.<br>Book a free consultation today and give your windows the upgrade they deserve!', 'null', 4, 2, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
