", \"public_id\": \"uploads/pp5xc6jxjxsacomlgz2c\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Blackout Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749807514/uploads/o2ub0qqhjtqc6xz9jzqw.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/o2ub0qqhjtqc6xz9jzqw\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Blackout Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749807533/uploads/utk1d877xhc51qmdkxk0.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/utk1d877xhc51qmdkxk0\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-07 07:56:52.957', '2025-12-01 11:32:51.767', '', 'Custom-made blackout curtains. Choose the fabrics of your choices, linings, and styles to give your living room a personalised feel.', 'Blackout Curtains Dubai | Total Light Control & Fast Installation', NULL, 'blackout-curtains', 'Blackout Curtains', '{"altText": "Blackout Curtains", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747735707/uploads/bozwierkyyqdktqfjsxe.webp", "public_id": "uploads/bozwierkyyqdktqfjsxe", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Total Darkness & Privacy with Blackout Curtains –<br>Free Consultation & Fast Installation!', 'Blackout curtains, total privacy', '{}', '
', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Blackout Curtains\", \"detail\": \"Blackout curtains are more than just a way to darken a room—they shape how a space feels and functions. Whether for better sleep, complete privacy, or insulation, blackout curtains serve a purpose beyond aesthetics. Unlike cheap blackout curtains that only soften light, our blackout fabrics completely block light from passing through the fabric. Perfect for bedrooms, nurseries, home theatres, and any space where light control truly matters.\"}","{\"name\": \"Designed for the Needs of Every Space\", \"detail\": \"The biggest misconception about blackout curtains is that they have to be thick, stiff, or heavy-looking. In reality, blackout fabric has a special coating onto the back of a curtain, meaning you can have almost any look you want, like a white blackout curtain while still getting the full blackout effect.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Blackout curtains must be measured and installed correctly to work as they should. Light may pass from the bottom or sides but our team will advise you of the best way to reduce the light penetration. With over 7,000 curtains installed annually, our team are happy to offer impartial advice and guidance to ensure the perfect curtains for your home. The Two Guys Home Furnishings team create blackout curtains precisely and according to the exact dimensions of your windows for a perfect drape, and total light control.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Some prefer fully coated blackout fabric, while others may want a lighter, dim-out option that softens rather than completely blocks light. Beyond custom sizing, we offer different lining options based on how much insulation, light-blocking, and sound reduction you need.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Blackout Curtains', 'Privacy protection', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Book your free consultation today and experience the future of smart living', 'Handcrafted by artisans with a passion for creativity, Two Guys Home F