', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Hotel Curtains\", \"detail\": \"Comfort For Every Guest & Elegance In Every Room. Why do we say comfort? Because the right curtain can shape the entire guest experience. The right curtains for hotels create a sense of luxury and privacy, setting the mood from the moment guests walk into the hotel room. Some guests need total blackout for restful sleep, some of them prefer sheer layers for soft daylight, and hotel owners need durable fabrics that withstand constant use. In lobbies, restaurants, and event spaces, luxury hotel curtains must be both decorative and functional, with heavier fabrics creating warmth and intimacy while lighter sheers maintain openness and flow. So, how to choose one?\"}","{\"name\": \"Better Coverage, Better Insulation, and a Richer, Elegant Look\", \"detail\": \"We offer a handpicked selection of premium fabrics, including plush velvets, airy voiles, textured weaves, and blackout options. Our team has a high standard when it comes to choosing durable fabric for our customers. We curated this collection to withstand daily use, making them the ideal choice for hospitality environments. We don’t compromise on quality, no matter the style or budget. With thousands of fabric options and endless customisation possibilities, we help our clients find curtains to enhance the look of their interiors while meeting their functional needs.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"We are not here to push a sale—we are here to help you make the right choice. Our team is made up of experts in fabric, design, and functionality, and every recommendation is made with your hotel’s long-term needs in mind. We are here to guide you through the process, from understanding fabric performance to choosing the right track system for smooth operation. We also specialise in smart automation integration. Our goal is to make it hassle-free from the moment you walk into our showroom for hotel curtains in Dubai to enhance the guest experience overall, not just something that looks good for a few months.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Hotel Curtains', 'Customisation Possibilities', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Book your free consultation today and experience the future of smart living', 'Handcrafted by artisans with a passion for creativity, Two Guys Home Furnishings help bring your imagination to reality with their best home decor services and products.', 'null', 4, 3, '', 70, 'PUBLISHED');
