ad/v1764071440/uploads/cqc88ghvgdtgwaxnaw5b.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/cqc88ghvgdtgwaxnaw5b\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-13 06:20:06.873', '2025-12-01 11:54:18.489', '', 'Custom-made, high-quality curtains for your home. You can choose from a variety of fabrics, linings, and styles.', 'Sheer Curtains Dubai | Light, Airy & Custom-Fitted for Your Home', NULL, 'sheer-curtains', 'Sheer Curtains', '{"altText": "Sheer Curtains", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747802814/uploads/eyzvyv3nep62djnf3ddb.webp", "public_id": "uploads/eyzvyv3nep62djnf3ddb", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Soft, Airy Sheer Curtains for Natural <br> Light – Free Home Visit & 2-Day Installation!', 'Curtains that welcome light', '{}', '
', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Sheer Curtains\", \"detail\": \"Sheer curtains can act as light filters, privacy enhancers, and room softeners. Unlike heavier drapes that block out light and enclose a space, sheers allow daylight to pass through while diffusing glare and creating a soft, natural glow. They add an airy, flowing quality to a room, making spaces feel larger, brighter, and more inviting. But not all sheer curtains are the same. It''s all about the weave, the weight, and the fibre content that decides how much light gets through, how they drape, and how they interact with natural movement in a room. They also help in reducing dust from entering through windows while allowing ventilation—a small but often overlooked benefit.\"}","{\"name\": \"Sheer Curtains: More Than Just Window Dressing\", \"detail\": \"Sheer curtains require precise installation to achieve their intended effect. Too short, and they look awkward. Too long, and they pool excessively, gathering dust. The right sheer curtain panel or track placement enhances their flow—mounted higher than the window frame, they create an illusion of height and openness. If paired with heavier curtains, double tracks or layered rods ensure smooth functionality without bunching or overcrowding. The way sheer curtains move matters too—light fabrics should glide effortlessly, creating soft ripples rather than stiff folds.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Off-the-shelf sheers often fail to deliver the right proportions, fabric weight, or tailored fit that a space truly needs. Every sheer curtain we make is measured, cut, and installed according to your window''s exact dimensions. Our in-house team of experts helps you choose the perfect sheer curtain fabric and colour, so you can get the right level of light diffusion, movement, and privacy. Then, the installation team takes care of every detail, from selecting the best track to adjusting the final length.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Sheer Curtains', ' Soft Natural Glow', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Book your free consultation today and experience the future of smart living', 'Handcrafted by artisans with a passion for creativity, Two Guys Home Furnishings help bring your imagination to reality with their best home decor services and products.', 'null', 4, 3, '', 16, 'PUBLISHED');
