', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Standard Curtains \", \"detail\": \"Standard curtains might sound simple, but they have the ability to frame your windows, shape the lighting coming from outside, and define the overall atmosphere. Whether they are light and breezy or rich and dramatic, they can create a feeling of cosiness and a sense of relaxation. The right curtains give privacy without making a space feel closed off. But not all standard curtains are the same. The standard curtain measurement, fabric, lining, and heading style completely change how they look and function.\"}","{\"name\": \"The Foundation of a Well-Dressed Home\", \"detail\": \"We have a huge collection of high-quality standard window curtains.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"We don’t believe in “one-size-fits-all” solutions; every home is different, and so is every window. You can visit our showroom in Al Quoz, or we can bring our showroom to your doorstep with our mobile teams. You can choose the fabric, the lining, and the heading type— a modern eyelet, a structured pinch pleat, or a relaxed pencil pleat.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Once you have decided everything, all you need to do is sit back, relax and let us take care of everything. And if you ever need them moved or reinstalled within 2 years, we take care of that too at no charge. Just a part of our after sales care pack, free with every order\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Standard Curtains', 'Perfect closure', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Book your free consultation today and experience the future of smart living', 'Handcrafted by artisans with a passion for creativity, Two Guys Home Furnishings help bring your imagination to reality with their best home decor services and products.', 'null', 4, 3, '', 16, 'PUBLISHED');
