s/u2clathrfc8781dmhfbj\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Duplex Blinds\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749800744/uploads/ihlkl0ritdfxpkwqtzko.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/ihlkl0ritdfxpkwqtzko\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Duplex Blinds\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749800745/uploads/h9bnueistcay9x09viw3.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/h9bnueistcay9x09viw3\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-13 07:22:57.854', '2025-12-01 11:16:49.486', '', 'Get custom-fit duplex blinds with sheer and blackout options with in-house production and a 5-year warranty. A free consultation service is available.', 'Made-to-Measure Duplex Blinds  | At Two Guys ', NULL, 'duplex-blinds', 'Duplex Blinds', '{"altText": "Duplex Blinds", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749800717/uploads/mx0xjnslv3jrswt7ln9s.webp", "public_id": "uploads/mx0xjnslv3jrswt7ln9s", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Custom Duplex Blinds in Dubai and<br>UAE – Designed for Comfort, Built to Last', 'Style and Comfort, in Every Blind', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Custom Duplex Blinds\", \"detail\": \"Duplex blinds, sometimes called \\\"zebra blinds\\\" or \\\"Day and Night blinds,\\\" consist of two layers of fabric, one solid and one sheer panel. Whether you want to welcome natural light or create a cosy, dimmed environment, these innovative blinds make it effortless. As you lower the blind, alternating fabric strips align to showcase either a solid block of colour or a stylish pattern of stripes. \"}","{\"name\": \"Custom-Fit Zebra Blinds Dubai with Free Installation \", \"detail\": \"At Two Guys, we specialise in duplex blinds; these smart window coverings are designed for homes and offices. They block UV rays, reduce glare, and improve energy efficiency, keeping your living room, office, meeting room, or kids'' bedroom comfortable in every season. Our zebra blinds for windows are simple to clean with a vacuum brush or damp cloth, making them hassle-free to maintain. We also have motorised zebra blind curtains aligned with smart home systems like Alexa and Google Assistant, giving you remote control operation.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"As a leading provider of zebra blinds in Dubai, Two Guys delivers custom-fit solutions with free installation, premium in-house production, and a 5-year warranty. With over 200 material choices, we ensure a perfect match for any interior.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Two Guys zebra blinds—crafted for your space.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Duplex Blinds', 'Blinds with  Two Layers of Fabrics', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Blinds Installation', 'Our team offers customised window coverings across Dubai, backed by a 5-year installation warranty.<br>Book a free consultation today and give your windows the upgrade they deserve!', 'null', 4, 2, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
