.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/dy5wvajyootmcwsvpghi\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Motorised Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749807341/uploads/of0s5ithkcwvytqrgjco.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/of0s5ithkcwvytqrgjco\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Motorised Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749807342/uploads/tqi2isw3i7gtprc2cemn.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/tqi2isw3i7gtprc2cemn\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-07 07:47:08.555', '2025-12-05 11:58:00.757', '', 'Custom-made motorised curtains. It''s time to upgrade your windows, with free installation and expert advice.', 'Motorised Curtains Dubai | Smart Curtains with Fast Installation', NULL, 'motorised-curtains', 'Motorised Curtains', '{"altText": "Motorised Curtains", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747742141/uploads/ralrjefc609ocuv63wgp.webp", "public_id": "uploads/ralrjefc609ocuv63wgp", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Smart Motorised Curtains for Easy Living –<br>Free Consultation & Quick Installation!', 'Smart curtains, effortless living', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Motorised Curtains\", \"detail\": \"No cords, no tugging, no uneven drapes-just smooth, silent movement at your fingertips. It''s not all about automation; manual curtains can''t match the precision of automated curtains. Every time they open and close, they do so perfectly aligned, creating a clean, polished look that stays consistent over time. They also extend the life of your curtains by eliminating wear and tear from pulling; that''s how the fabric stays in place and the pleats remain crisp. With motorised curtains, you can bring comfort, beauty, and control into every moment of your day.\"}","{\"name\": \"How to choose curtains for living room?\", \"detail\": \"Here at Two Guys Home Furnishings, we know how important it is to have motorised curtains that fit your home, your style, and your needs. If you want to set them to open with sunrise, close with sunset, or adjust at any time throughout the day, you can do it with Alexa, Google Home, or a remote/wall switch.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"You pick the fabric, the pleat style, and the level of opacity, and we do the rest. What else makes us different? We use trusted brands like Somfy, Nice, and Motion, so you know you''re getting a quality product. With whisper-quiet motors, you can maintain a quiet home whether using a remote control, a wall switch, an app, or a voice command. With no bulky accessories, no exposed wires, just a sleek, seamless solution that blends beautifully into your home.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our expert team will do a precise installation, so the curtains glide smoothly without resistance. And if you ever want adjustments, we offer ongoing support and reinstallation services, too.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Motorised Curtains', 'Smart, Stunning Look', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Book your free consultation today and experience the future of smart living', 'Handcrafted by artisans with a passion for creativity, Two Guys Home Furnishings help bring your imagination to reality with their best home decor services and products.', 'null', 4, 3, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
