ral light.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"We offer motorised skylight blinds, which operate effortlessly with a remote control or wall switch. Whether you need flat roof skylight blinds or flat roof window blinds, our innovative solutions provide smooth, hassle-free light control. \"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"We specialise in made-to-measure Velux skylight blinds and custom-fit options designed to complement your Velux roof windows. With over 750+ 5-star reviews, Two Guys is a trusted name in window coverings, delivering exceptional quality, service, and innovation.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Visit our showroom or book a free consultation today!\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Skylight Blinds', 'Every Window Solution', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Blinds Installation', 'Our team offers customised window coverings across Dubai, backed by a 5-year installation warranty.<br>Book a free consultation today and give your windows the upgrade they deserve!', 'null', 4, 2, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
