', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Tracked Shutters: Flexible, Functional, and Made to Glide.\", \"detail\": \"For any home featuring expansive glass, be it big windows, patio doors, or sliding doors, tracked window shutters are the ideal, modern solution. Instead of being constrained by hinges, these stylish panels are engineered to glide smoothly along a secure track, making them effortless to use, even across very wide openings. They are the perfect blend of practical design and elegant style, giving you quick, complete control over light, airflow, and privacy.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Tracked shutters are incredibly versatile. Use them in living rooms, bedrooms with balcony access, or as a sophisticated room divider in open-plan spaces. They glide effortlessly, making them ideal for high-traffic areas and ensuring unblocked access whenever you need it.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"We offer two main types to suit your space:\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"<b>Bi-fold Shutters: </b>These panels are hinged together and fold neatly to the side, stacking compactly to fully expose the window or door.</br><b>By-pass Shutters: </b>Panels in this style slide past each other on parallel tracks, maintaining coverage of some portion of the opening, which is perfect for continuous, large-scale window walls.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"At Two Guys Home Furnishings, our made-to-measure shutters are built to last. Every investment in our Tracked window shutters is protected by a comprehensive 5-year warranty. From the moment you order, you can expect installation to be completed efficiently within 6–8 weeks.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Tracked Shutters', 'Explore Our Materials, Colours, and Full-Length Design Options', 'Quick & Reliable Service', 'Stop Struggling with Wide Openings', 'Ready for a sleek, modern solution for your patio doors or large windows? Our experts will show you how tracked shutters glide perfectly in your home.', 'null', 4, 4, '', NULL,