', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Bay Window Shutters For Angled or Curved Windows\", \"detail\": \"Our Premium Bay window shutters are elegant window coverings that are especially made for bay-style windows, the ones that extend outward and create a beautiful space filled with natural light. Whether your bay windows are angled, curved, or square, our team designs shutters that fit perfectly and enhance your home’s overall look.\"}","{\"name\": \"Crafted to Suit Every Window – Choose What Fits Your Style\", \"detail\": \"When it comes to bay window shutters, choosing the right material matters. At Two Guys, we offer three premium options — MDF, Paulownia, and Basswood, each designed to suit your home’s style, size, and sunlight exposure. Our MDF material is ideal for smaller bay windows or rooms with limited direct sunlight, such as bedrooms or hallways. Paulownia works best for medium to large bay windows in living rooms or dining areas. They’re lightweight yet strong, resist warping, and bring a beautiful, natural wood texture that adds warmth and charm to your space.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our Basswood shutters are perfect for wide or tall bay windows or areas with strong sunlight. They offer a luxurious, elegant finish and lasting durability,  great for homeowners who want both strength and sophistication. Each material is custom-crafted to fit your bay windows perfectly, giving your home a timeless, stylish, and long-lasting finish.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Bay Window Shutters', 'Perfect Solution for Bay Windows', 'Fast & Professional Bay Window Shutter Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Bay Window Shutters', 'Enhance your bay windows with beautifully crafted, custom-made shutters, designed for a perfect fit, timeless style, and lasting quality. At Two Guys, we offer free home consultation, precise measurements, and expert installation, all backed by a 05-year warranty. Call us today at +971 50 597 4495 and give your bay windows the elegant upgrade they deserve!', 'null', 4, 4, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
