6/uploads/vwlbzpxfcxvueh0tukho.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/vwlbzpxfcxvueh0tukho\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Special Shape Shutters\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749808878/uploads/zdyqg6fifreyeuakztfp.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/zdyqg6fifreyeuakztfp\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Special Shape Shutters\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1764054246/uploads/b2mtwfkhwk5yspfaxqiu.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/b2mtwfkhwk5yspfaxqiu\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-07 09:58:32.952', '2025-12-02 05:55:13.316', '', 'Discover beautifully crafted shutters for unique window shapes, arched, round, or triangular. Premium materials and expert installation in Dubai.
', 'Custom Special Shape Shutters Dubai | Two Guys UAE', NULL, 'special-shape-shutters', 'Special Shape Shutters', '{"altText": "Special Shape Shutters", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747809131/uploads/sbxyv7b1mxixkugtoeg9.webp", "public_id": "uploads/sbxyv7b1mxixkugtoeg9", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Special Shape Shutters Designed to Fit<br>Unique Windows in Dubai, UAE', 'Elegant Shutters', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Special Shape Shutters for Any Window Shape\", \"detail\": \"Not all windows are the same, and that’s what makes your home special! Our Special Shape Shutters are designed to fit a variety of window types, including arched, circular, triangular, and angled windows. Each shutter is custom-made to match the unique design of your window, providing a neat, stylish, and elegant finish. At Two Guys, we make sure every curve and edge fits perfectly. These shutters not only look beautiful but also give you better control over light, privacy, and heat, making them a smart and stylish choice for your interiors. \"}","{\"name\": \"Made for Every Unique Window – Choose What Fits Your Style\", \"detail\": \"Choosing the right material for your special shape shutters makes all the difference in how they look and last. At Two Guys, we offer three top-quality options, MDF, Paulownia, and Basswood, each suited to different window shapes and home styles. MDF shutters are perfect for smaller or less exposed-shaped windows, like round or half-moon designs. They offer a smooth, clean finish and are great if you’re looking for a stylish option.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Paulownia shutters are lightweight and durable, making them ideal for angled or arched windows. Their natural wood texture adds warmth and character while staying strong and resistant to warping. Our Basswood shutters are the premium choice for large or statement-shaped windows that deserve a high-end touch. They’re elegant, sturdy, and built to last. Each shutter is custom-crafted to fit your window’s unique shape perfectly.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Special Shape Shutters', 'Perfect Solution for Special Shape Windows', 'Fast & Professional Special Shape Shutter Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Custom-Shaped Shutters', 'Enhance your unique windows with beautifully crafted, custom-made shutters designed to fit any shape. At Two Guys, we offer free home consultations, accurate measurements, and expert installation, all backed by a 5-year warranty for lasting quality and peace of mind.</br>Call us today at +971 50 597 4495 and give your windows the perfect finish they deserve!', 'null', 4, 4, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
