scop8lvbz8b9.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/i3ly723jscop8lvbz8b9\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Cafe Style Shutters\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747805536/uploads/scxfuqe2yjebp5asqh7z.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/scxfuqe2yjebp5asqh7z\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Cafe Style Shutters\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747805538/uploads/av1zcfttuvtmzpcn2krz.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/av1zcfttuvtmzpcn2krz\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Cafe Style Shutters\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747805540/uploads/cbd8fsllc1yhvh6iq2qw.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/cbd8fsllc1yhvh6iq2qw\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-13 10:33:25.834', '2025-12-02 05:55:00.607', '', 'Buy Café Style shutters for the perfect blend of light and privacy. Half-window design is ideal for kitchens & street-facing rooms. Made-to-measure.
', 'Café Style Shutters: Half-Height Design for Light & Privacy', NULL, 'cafe-style-shutters', 'Cafe Style Shutters', '{"altText": "Cafe Style Shutters", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747805507/uploads/ff13zs9qwsaxdsrfxs4b.webp", "public_id": "uploads/ff13zs9qwsaxdsrfxs4b", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Café Style Shutters: European</br>Elegance Meets Natural Light', 'Privacy, Perfectly Balanced', '{}', '
', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Café Style Shutters: The Perfect Blend of Light and Privacy\", \"detail\": \"If you''re looking for the sweet spot between enjoying natural light and maintaining your home''s privacy, Café Style shutters are the answer. Inspired by classic European cafés, these shutters cover only the lower half of your windows. This smart design gives you the essential privacy you need at eye-level while leaving the top of the window completely open for an abundance of daylight.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our café window shutters are ideal for street-facing rooms such as kitchens, dining areas, and home offices. They offer a refined, timeless look while ensuring you can enjoy plenty of sunlight without feeling exposed.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"These café-style plantation shutters feature adjustable slats, giving you even finer control over light and view. We craft them using durable materials to suit any space:\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"<b>Basswood: </b>For a premium, classic look.</br><b>PVC: </b>Ideal for high-humidity areas.</br><b>MDF: </b>A strong, value-focused option.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"All our wood café shutters are made to measure by Two Guys Home Furnishings, guaranteeing a custom fit. Every investment in our Half Café shutters is protected by a comprehensive 5-year warranty. From the moment you order, you can expect installation to be completed efficiently within 6–8 weeks.\"}"}', '{"{\"name\": \"Can I have different-sized slats on café-style shutters? \", \"detail\": \"We offer several slat sizes, from 63mm up to 114mm. Bigger slats let in more light when open and give a more contemporary look. Smaller ones offer more privacy when tilted and have a more traditional feel.\"}","{\"name\": \"Do café-style shutters work with sash windows?\", \"detail\": \"They''re perfect for sash windows! The half-height design complements the traditional sash window look. However, we can also sort you out with tier-on-tier shutters that follow the sash design if you prefer full coverage with separate controls.\"}","{\"name\": \"Will café style shutters make my room dark? \", \"detail\": \"Not at all! That''s their beauty—they keep the top half of your window open, so you get plenty of natural light flooding in. You also get more light than full shutters even when the slats are closed because there''s less coverage.\"}"}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Café Style Shutters', 'Explore Our Materials, Colours, and Full-Length Design Options', 'Quick & Reliable Service', 'Find Your Perfect Privacy Balance', 'Ready to enjoy natural daylight without feeling exposed? Our experts will show you how Café Style shutters can transform your street-facing rooms with classic style.', 'null', 4, 4, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
