loads/qqouy939p4srtvocu63d\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Vertical Blinds\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1764224794/uploads/htt02wbo4exlyig9ud2n.png\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/htt02wbo4exlyig9ud2n\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-13 10:00:01.347', '2025-12-02 09:31:47.703', '', 'Shop high-quality vertical blinds. Perfect for large windows, sliding doors, and offices, our custom blinds are easy to maintain. Visit us today! 
', 'Vertical Blinds for Homes & Offices | Custom Made & Easy to Use', NULL, 'vertical-blinds', 'Vertical Blinds', '{"altText": "Vertical Blinds", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747130374/uploads/qusn6fr7zjjxanji8n2y.webp", "public_id": "uploads/qusn6fr7zjjxanji8n2y", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Vertical Blinds for Light Control and Privacy', 'Blinds That Fit Your Lifestyle', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Vertical Blinds\", \"detail\": \"Vertical blinds are window coverings that are made up of long vertical slats (called vanes). They hang from a top track and can be tilted or drawn to the side to control light and privacy. Unlike heavy drapes, they create a sleek and understated finish, ideal for both contemporary and classic interiors.\"}","{\"name\": \"Custom-Made for the Perfect Fit\", \"detail\": \"Pairing  vertical blinds with curtains gives you the best of both worlds: soft fabric drapes for warmth and elegance and structured vertical slats for precise light control. This layered setup is perfect for everything from sliding doors and large windows to compact spaces, offering stylish flexibility from day to night.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"At Two Guys, our  made-to-measure vertical blinds are crafted for a flawless fit. We offer free home visits to ensure accurate measurements, removing the uneven gaps and awkward lengths caused by off-the-shelf sizes. Proper installation is key—if the track isn’t aligned or the spacing is off, slats may drag or stack unevenly. That’s why our expert installation team ensures your blinds  are fitted and tested for smooth operation right from the start. \"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Over time, window treatments may need a refresh. Instead of replacing the entire setup, you can simply update the vertical blind slats. It’s a cost-effective way to give your space a clean, updated look without the need for full renovation. Whether you''re installing new vertical blinds or upgrading existing ones, we’re here to help you find the perfect fit—today and for years to come.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"<b>Visit our showroom or book a free consultation today!</b>\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Vertical Blinds', 'Every Window Solution', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Blinds Installation', 'Our team offers customised window coverings across Dubai, backed by a 5-year installation warranty.<br>Book a free consultation today and give your windows the upgrade they deserve!', 'null', 4, 2, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
