/wrfocqyld4vlsf9jousy\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Home Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747738365/uploads/al7x3l6gbaywrtyom9lb.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/al7x3l6gbaywrtyom9lb\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Home Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747738369/uploads/jsu6ka1ocr8cfxfdq52a.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/jsu6ka1ocr8cfxfdq52a\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-07 09:18:53.264', '2025-12-02 11:37:34.119', '', 'Custom-made, high-quality curtains for your home. You can choose from a variety of fabrics, linings, and styles.', 'Home Curtains Dubai | 3,000+ Fabrics & Free Expert Advice', NULL, 'home-curtains', 'Home Curtains', '{"altText": "Home Curtains", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747738336/uploads/ln9wprlwlaufs7xrbmc3.webp", "public_id": "uploads/ln9wprlwlaufs7xrbmc3", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Beautiful Home Curtains, Custom-Fitted – Free<br>Expert Advice & Hassle-Free Installation!', 'Your curtain, your style', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Home Curtains\", \"detail\": \"They''re more than just fabric hanging over windows; they create ambience, let light flow, and make a room feel more comfortable. A good curtain controls light, manages privacy, insulates against heat and cold, and sets the tone for an entire room. A lot goes into choosing the right home curtains, like fabric weight, lining, pleat style, heading type, and installation method. There is a lot to consider, from the texture to the way the fabric moves when drawn.\"}","{\"name\": \"Home Curtains: More Than Just Window Dressing\", \"detail\": \"Different fabrics are good for different rooms. Having blackout or dim-out options in the bedroom makes it easier to sleep, while sheer fabrics in the living room let in natural light. Fabrics that are breathable, washable, and resist humidity are great for kitchens. Linen drapes easily, but is prone to creases. The velvet absorbs sound and acts as insulation. Fabric weaves and density also affect how curtains hang, how much air they trap, and how they interact with artificial and natural light. Our experts will hand-hold you through the entire process.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Different fabrics are good for different rooms. Having blackout or dim-out options in the bedroom makes it easier to sleep, while sheer fabrics in the living room let in natural light. Fabrics that are breathable, washable, and resist humidity are great for kitchens. Linen drapes easily, but is prone to creases. The velvet absorbs sound and acts as insulation. Fabric weaves and density also affect how curtains hang, how much air they trap, and how they interact with artificial and natural light. Our experts will hand-hold you through the entire process.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Home curtains are more than a design choice—they impact comfort, energy efficiency, and even how sound travels in a space. That’s why we take the time to get every detail right. Because when modern home curtains are done properly, they don’t just frame a window—they transform a home.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Home Curtains', 'Manages Privacy', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Book your free consultation today and experience the future of smart living', 'Handcrafted by artisans with a passion for creativity, Two Guys Home Furnishings help bring your imagination to reality with their best home decor services and products.', 'null', 4, 3, '', 70, 'PUBLISHED');
