lso envelops them in a subtle velvet embrace.\"}"}', '{"{\"name\": \"For Homes\", \"detail\": \"<ul> <li>Living Room Elegance: Elevate your living spaces with Soft Velvet Finish wall paints that exude warmth and sophistication. The soft texture adds depth to your walls, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere.</li> <li>Bedroom Serenity: Transform your bedroom into a serene retreat with walls coated in soft velvet. Experience the gentle embrace of these paints as you unwind and relax.</li> <li>Dining Room Charm: Make your dining area a feast for the eyes with the gentle shimmer of Soft Velvet Finish. Whether it&rsquo;s a cozy family dinner or a grand celebration, these paints set the perfect ambiance.</li> </ul>\"}"}', '', '{"{\"name\": \"For Offices\", \"detail\": \"<ul> <li><strong>Office Sophistication:</strong> Impress clients and create an elegant workspace with Soft Velvet Finish wall paints. These paints convey professionalism and sophistication.</li> <li><strong>Conference Room Appeal:</strong> Elevate your meeting rooms with the soft, velvety touch of these paints. They provide a subtle backdrop for productive discussions and presentations.</li> </ul>\"}"}', '{"imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747113325/uploads/apgnbd6sidwogtxvwxfu.webp", "public_id": "uploads/apgnbd6sidwogtxvwxfu", "resource_type": "image"}', '', '', 'Quick Installation', 'WPC Flooring Installation <br/> All Over Dubai UAE', 'Not sure where to start <br/> on your next WPC?', 'null', 6, 11, '', NULL, 'DRAFT');
