75nudxbt3tosfwoo.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/g5b975nudxbt3tosfwoo\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Living Room Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747741090/uploads/rxbvq2ntm8kzbtcrzo9l.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/rxbvq2ntm8kzbtcrzo9l\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Living Room Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747741091/uploads/gaaloqknjddq0vwwymuu.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/gaaloqknjddq0vwwymuu\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-13 06:28:08.938', '2025-12-02 11:37:48.689', '', 'Custom-made living room curtains. You can choose from thousands of fabrics choices, linings, and styles to give your living room a personalised feel.', 'Living Room Curtains Dubai | With 3,000+ Fabric Choices', NULL, 'living-room-curtains', 'Living Room Curtains', '{"altText": "Living Room Curtains", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747741067/uploads/ala7dcevk6ut65jgjq7c.webp", "public_id": "uploads/ala7dcevk6ut65jgjq7c", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Custom Living Room Curtains, Made for Your <br> Space – 3,000+ Fabrics & Free Installation!', 'Premium curtains, perfect fit', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Living Room Curtains\", \"detail\": \"Let''s find curtains for the most lived-in space in your home. The right curtains control light, privacy, temperature, and even acoustics, all while complementing your furniture and decor. A room bathed in natural light may need sheer curtains that soften the brightness without blocking the view. A space used for movie nights and relaxation may require blackout or dim-out fabrics to create the perfect ambience. If insulation is a concern, thermal-lined curtains can help maintain warmth in winter and keep out heat in summer. Whether you want a grand, luxurious drape or a clean, minimal finish, the choice of fabric, pleat style, and lining all play a crucial role in how your living room feels.\"}","{\"name\": \"How to choose curtains for living room?\", \"detail\": \"We make every curtain to your exact window size, ceiling height, and interior style, this is how we ensure a perfect fit every time for every client. Whether you prefer the structured elegance of pinch pleats, the soft flow of wave curtains, or the modern simplicity of eyelets, we help you choose the right living room curtain design to feel like it belongs in your room.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"We believe in honest, expert advice. Our team takes the time to understand your light preferences, fabric choices, and functional needs before making recommendations. If you’re unsure whether you need bright curtains for living room, how to layer sheer curtains with heavier drapes, or which pleat style will best suit your home, we guide you through every detail so you make the right choice.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Modern curtains for the living room deserve precise installation. Our professional fitting team always receive excellent reviews for measuring accurately, spacing perfectly, and hanging correctly, with smooth operation and a flawless drape, unlike ready made living room curtains. We also offer reinstallation services within two years of the first installation, if you decide to move your curtains to another place or refresh your windows.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Living Room Curtains', 'Minimal Finish', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Book your free consultation today and experience the future of smart living', 'Handcrafted by artisans with a passion for creativity, Two Guys Home Furnishings help bring your imagination to reality with their best home decor services and products.', 'null', 4, 3, '', 70, 'PUBLISHED');
