f. Because it is tightly woven to block UV rays, you can still see outside. \"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"As a result, you may enjoy the view without sacrificing comfort. Our sunscreen vertical blinds are perfect for spaces with large windows, including living rooms or workplaces, where you need to balance light and privacy. \"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our sunscreen blinds save energy since they reduce the need for air conditioning by keeping your room cooler. Our motorised sunscreen blinds with remote control, Alexa, or Google options allow you to use all the benefits of natural light without the drawbacks of too much sunshine. So, take advantage and visit our showroom or book an appointment with free home visits and installations.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Visit our showroom or book a free consultation today!\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Sunscreen Blinds', 'Perfect Blinds for Outside View', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Blinds Installation', 'Our team offers customised window coverings across Dubai, backed by a 5-year installation warranty.<br>Book a free consultation today and give your windows the upgrade they deserve!', 'null', 4, 2, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
