hey also help to regulate temperature and protect your furnishings from harsh sunlight. \"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"You can enhance your blinds'' aesthetic with blackout, sunscreen, and transparent roller blinds. You can choose roller blinds based on practical features like easy-wipe, fire-retardant, and moisture-resistant fabrics. For added comfort and convenience, you can also opt for a motorised system powered by Somfy, allowing you to control your blinds with ease.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Enjoy free home visits and free installation with every order!\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Visit our showroom or book a free consultation today!\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Roller Blinds', 'Every Window Solution', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Blinds Installation', 'Our team offers customised window coverings across Dubai, backed by a 5-year installation warranty.</br> Book a free consultation today and give your windows the upgrade they deserve!', 'null', 4, 2, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
