ds/fijufjaffl3o5utqnjne.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/fijufjaffl3o5utqnjne\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Pencil Pleat Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747744833/uploads/vroztmwrxx59av2acash.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/vroztmwrxx59av2acash\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Pencil Pleat Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747744835/uploads/inxucdthabdhfiujpfwc.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/inxucdthabdhfiujpfwc\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-13 06:58:11.332', '2025-12-02 05:42:16.007', '', 'High-quality, custom-made pencil pleat curtains. We offer a variety of fabrics, linings, and styles for you to choose from.', 'Pencil Pleat Curtains Dubai | Custom-Made & Installed in 2 to 3 Days', NULL, 'pencil-pleat-curtains', 'Pencil Pleat Curtains', '{"altText": "Pencil Pleat Curtains", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747744806/uploads/kjn718n2hokmb4nagxse.webp", "public_id": "uploads/kjn718n2hokmb4nagxse", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Custom-Made Pencil Pleat Curtains – Free <br> Expert Advice & Installation in 2-3 Days!', 'Perfect pleats, perfect curtains', '{}', '
', 'Pencil Pleat Curtains
', '{"{\"name\": \"Pencil Pleat Curtains\", \"detail\": \"There''s nothing more classic or versatile than pencil pleat curtains, which create soft, even folds in any room. Their neatly gathered pleats look great in both traditional and modern decor, adding height and depth to your interior. Unlike structured curtain styles, pencil pleats let you choose whether you want a relaxed, casual drape or one with a bit more finesse. With the perfect fit and easy to hang, pencil pleat curtain hooks work on tracks and poles.\"}","{\"name\": \"Simple, Functional, and Beautiful in Every Light\", \"detail\": \"If you want curtains that look full, adjust easily, and provide just the right amount of privacy and light control, pencil pleats are ideal. Their warmth and softness don''t compromise on practicality or ease of maintenance.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Pencil pleat curtains without lining are lighter and more breathable, letting natural light in while providing privacy at the same time. While lined pencil pleat curtains have both elegance and practicality, including better insulation and light control.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"There''s a variety of high-quality fabrics in our pencil pleat collection, from linens and light voiles to velvets and blackout linings. Then we are passionate about customisation - we let you pick the fabric, the lining, the heading width, and the length to make it exactly how you need it, unlike ready-made curtains.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"We also understand that installing curtains is just as important as choosing them. Each sophisticated and modern pencil pleat curtain is hung by our expert fitting team with precision, so the pleats fall naturally and beautifully. With free consultations, in-home measurements, and professional installation, we make sure your curtains do more than just cover your windows. \"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Pencil Pleat Curtains', 'Perfect Pleated Style', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Book your free consultation today and experience the future of smart living', 'Handcrafted by artisans with a passion for creativity, Two Guys Home Furnishings help bring your imagination to reality with their best home decor services and products.', 'null', 4, 3, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
