/ke0q3ktjbjsnpo43zhkc\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Wave Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747803575/uploads/pomiwlexwggyply8knlu.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/pomiwlexwggyply8knlu\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Wave Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747803576/uploads/lc1brjsx1be3tg7e1etn.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/lc1brjsx1be3tg7e1etn\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-13 06:50:41.691', '2025-12-02 05:53:28.587', '', 'Custom-made living room curtains. You can choose from thousands of fabrics choices, linings, and styles to give your living room a personalised feel.', 'Wave Curtains Dubai | Smooth, Modern Look with Free Installation', NULL, 'wave-curtains', 'Wave Curtains', '{"altText": "Wave Curtains", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747803551/uploads/exvzliqzazcpc0ok3vp9.webp", "public_id": "uploads/exvzliqzazcpc0ok3vp9", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Stylish Wave Curtains for a Smooth, Modern Look <br> – Free Expert Advice & Custom Fitting!', 'Curtains that float beautifully', '{}', '
', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Wave Curtains\", \"detail\": \"Wave curtains are different from traditional styles. Instead of stiff pleats or gathered fabric, they fall in smooth, uniformed folds . The secret is in the track system, which holds the fabric in a fixed rhythm, creating a clean and continuous wave effect like ripplefold curtains. Unlike standard curtains that need adjusting to look right, wave fold curtains always sit neatly, whether open or closed. This makes them ideal for modern spaces, floor-to-ceiling windows, and anywhere that needs a balance of softness and structure without clutter.\"}","{\"name\": \"Smooth, Modern Window Coverings\", \"detail\": \"Wave curtains rely on fabric weight and drape. Lighter fabrics, like sheers, create soft, airy movement, perfect for diffusing daylight without blocking it completely. Heavier fabrics hold their shape more firmly, giving a more structured look while offering better privacy and insulation.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Standard-sized curtains often lose their wave effect over time, either looking too loose or too stiff. We custom-make each set based on the exact window width, track position, and fabric weight to maintain the ideal shape.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Getting wave curtains right isn’t just about picking a fabric and hanging it up. It’s about understanding how they move, how they shape a room, and how they interact with light. Our team looks at every detail—from how the fabric falls to how the track aligns—so that once they’re up, they feel like they’ve always belonged. If you move within 2 years, we’ll even uninstall and re-install in your new place absolutely free of charge (alterations are chargeable, but fairly nominal amounts)\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Wave Curtains', ' Smooth Uniform Folds', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Book your free consultation today and experience the future of smart living', 'Handcrafted by artisans with a passion for creativity, Two Guys Home Furnishings help bring your imagination to reality with their best home decor services and products.', 'null', 4, 3, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
