', 'Aluminium Venetian blinds | Hassle-Free Installation', NULL, 'aluminium-venetian-blinds', 'Aluminium Blinds', '{"altText": "Aluminium Blinds", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749722409/uploads/ulvfykpns067wbp0xpyw.webp", "public_id": "uploads/ulvfykpns067wbp0xpyw", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Custom Aluminium Venetian Blinds</br> for Modern Homes & Offices', 'Blinds That Make Life Easier', '{}', '
', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Aluminum Venetian blinds\", \"detail\": \"When it comes to window coverings, the choices can be overwhelming, but you can never go wrong with a classic design like our Aluminium Venetian blinds, which are a popular type of window covering made from horizontal slats of lightweight aluminum. These metal slats are connected by cords or fabric tapes and can be tilted to control the amount of light and privacy in a room. You can also raise or lower the entire blind as needed.\"}","{\"name\": \"Aluminium Venetian blinds Dubai – Hassle-free Installation\", \"detail\": \"At Two Guys Home Furnishings, we offer Aluminium Venetian blinds for modern homes and offices. These custom-made blinds allow you to adjust the slats and create a perfect ambience for homes and offices.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our aluminium window blinds are crafted from high-quality materials, making them lightweight and easy to clean. Our blinds are resistant to moisture, mould, and dust, which makes them ideal for kitchens, bathrooms, conservatories, and balconies. \"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Additionally, their thermal insulation properties help to regulate indoor temperature, keeping spaces cool in the summer and warm in the winter for year-round comfort. Our aluminium blinds come in various colours and finishes, such as white Venetian blinds. They complement various interior styles, from minimalist and industrial to classic and bold. They are perfect for standard windows, sliding doors, and terrace windows. We also offer a 5-year warranty on all mechanical parts and labour, so schedule your free consultation today.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Visit our showroom or book a free consultation today!\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Aluminium Venetian Blinds', 'Perfect Solution for all Windows', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Blinds Installation', 'Our team offers customised window coverings across Dubai, backed by a 5-year installation warranty.</br> Book a free consultation today and give your windows the upgrade they deserve!', 'null', 4, 2, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
