ounds 45 AED per linear meter\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Collection', 'Fast moving WPC Flooring <br> Decking products', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Book your free consultation today and experience the future of smart living', 'Handcrafted by artisans with a passion for creativity, Two Guys Home Furnishings help bring your imagination to reality with their best home decor services and products.', 'null', 7, 20, '', 3, 'PUBLISHED');
