', 'Solid Panel Shutters Dubai | Custom Privacy Shutters', NULL, 'solid-panel-shutters', 'Solid Panel Shutters', '{"altText": "Solid Panel Shutters", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747807619/uploads/jopiovcgazj3ybd3cw8s.webp", "public_id": "uploads/jopiovcgazj3ybd3cw8s", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Solid Panel Shutters: Classic Elegance and</br> Complete Privacy for Every Home in Dubai, UAE', 'Custom Fit Shutters', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Solid Panel Shutters for Every Windows\", \"detail\": \"Our Solid Panel Shutters are perfect for homeowners who love a classic, elegant style with maximum privacy and insulation. Unlike louvered shutters, these come with fully solid panels that completely block light when closed, making them ideal for bedrooms, media rooms, and private living areas. You can open them during the day for natural sunlight, or close them at night for peace, comfort, and complete seclusion.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"At Two Guys, each Solid Panel Shutter is custom-made to fit your window perfectly, whether flat, raised, or molded panels, offering a flawless finish that enhances your home’s character. \"}","{\"name\": \"Crafted for Style and Strength – Choose the Material That Fits Your Space\", \"detail\": \"Our Solid Panel Shutters are built for durability and elegance. We offer three top-quality materials, MDF, Paulownia, and Basswood — each suited for different rooms and styles. Our MDF Solid Panel Shutters are perfect for living rooms, hallways, or home offices. They offer a clean, smooth look with great value. They’re durable and easy to maintain, making them an excellent choice for high-traffic areas or those seeking practical style.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Our Paulownia Solid Panel Shutters are ideal for larger or upper-floor windows. They’re great for sun-facing rooms, offering natural insulation while maintaining a soft, warm aesthetic that suits every decor. If you want a truly premium finish, Basswood is the perfect choice. Ideal for bedrooms, lounges, and feature windows, it combines elegance, strength, and refined wood grain, giving your space a high-end, timeless feel that lasts for years. No matter which material you select, our Solid Panel Shutters are designed for lasting durability, superior privacy, and timeless style.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Solid Panel Shutters', ' A Perfect Finish for a Peaceful Home', 'Fast & Professional Solid Panel Shutter Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Solid Panel Shutters', 'At Two Guys, we create custom-crafted shutters that combine traditional charm with modern style. Enjoy free home consultations, accurate measurements, and expert installation, all backed by a 5-year warranty for lasting confidence and peace of mind.</br>Call us today at +971 50 597 4495 and add timeless elegance and complete privacy to your home with Solid Panel Shutters by Two Guys.', 'null', 4, 4, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
