f8nlnn9c7ehmywhbpws.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/xf8nlnn9c7ehmywhbpws\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Honeycomb Blinds\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1763976070/uploads/ovcjng21zgda0teiwhwu.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/ovcjng21zgda0teiwhwu\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Honeycomb Blinds\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1763976071/uploads/g2pev5lgtinl4xups4be.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/g2pev5lgtinl4xups4be\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Honeycomb Blinds\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1763976072/uploads/dmcbowjho9hokytcnwdw.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/dmcbowjho9hokytcnwdw\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-13 07:17:02.067', '2025-12-01 11:20:28.536', '', 'Get custom honeycomb blinds at Two Guys with cordless, motorised, or remote-controlled options. In-house production with a free consultation.', 'Honeycomb blinds | 2-year uninstall and reinstall service free', NULL, 'colby-honeycomb-blinds', 'Honeycomb Blinds', '{"altText": "Honeycomb Blinds", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747723067/uploads/dkklldlkrgulb1oyhlbg.webp", "public_id": "uploads/dkklldlkrgulb1oyhlbg", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Custom Honeycomb Blinds in Dubai – </br>Smart Insulation, Stylish Design', 'Blinds That Work Around You', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Custom Honeycomb Blinds\", \"detail\": \"Honeycomb blinds, also known as cellular shades, are designed with a unique cellular structure. Each cell has honeycomb-shaped pockets that trap air in the window. The word ‘honeycomb blinds’ is derived from the structure of the window dressing.\"}","{\"name\": \"Honeycomb Blinds: Stylish & Smart Fit for Windows\", \"detail\": \"We at Two Guys have unique, custom honeycomb blinds that trap air, helping to regulate indoor temperatures. Beyond insulation, honeycomb window blinds provide multi-layered fabric that prevents visibility from the outside, ensuring a secure and private environment. Depending on your preference, you can choose our translucent cellular blinds that gently filter light or blackout honeycomb blinds that block out all external light, making them ideal for bedrooms, nurseries, and media rooms.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Another key advantage of honeycomb pleated blinds is their noise-reducing properties. By absorbing external sounds, they create a quieter, more peaceful atmosphere. Our honeycomb blinds come in multiple operating options, including cordless honeycomb blinds, motorised, and remote-controlled systems. \"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"This eliminates safety risks from cords for children and pets while providing effortless operation at the touch of a button. Our honeycomb blinds for windows are a smart and stylish solution for any home or office. We take pride in our in-house production, with a free 2-year uninstall and reinstall service in case you move, so get a free consultation today.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Visit our showroom or book a free consultation today!\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Honeycomb Blinds', 'Design with Cellular Shades', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Blinds Installation', 'Our team offers customised window coverings across Dubai, backed by a 5-year installation warranty.<br>Book a free consultation today and give your windows the upgrade they deserve!', 'null', 4, 2, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
