', 'Custom Sheer Horizon Blinds in Dubai |  Smart Control Blinds', NULL, 'sheer-horizon-blinds', 'Sheer Horizon Blinds', '{"imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749801203/uploads/qa1r5tqjbttvyjivxw5y.webp", "public_id": "uploads/qa1r5tqjbttvyjivxw5y", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Custom Sheer Horizon Blinds with Free </br>Installation in Dubai and the UAE', 'Light, Shade, and Perfect Blinds', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Sheer Horizon Blinds\", \"detail\": \"Sheer Horizon Blinds are completely new artistic window coverings that are distinct from all other available products. These blinds have soft fabric slats placed between two sheer layers to gently filter light. Our Sheer window blinds are available in a variety of materials, including a semi-blackout that allows for even more privacy and light control. \"}","{\"name\": \"Stylish Sheer Blinds: Tailored for Your Home\", \"detail\": \"We at Two Guys have Sheer blinds for windows that allow soft, diffused light to brighten your space while maintaining a clear outdoor view by creating a serene and inviting ambiance. We designed our sheer blinds for home or rental properties and offices.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"We have a wide selection of sheer fabrics. Whether you prefer neutral tones for a soft, airy feel or bolder shades for a statement look, our custom-made sheer window coverings are designed to suit your preferences.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"For modern convenience, our Sheer Blinds come with smart control options, allowing you to adjust them effortlessly using a remote, smartphone, or voice commands through Alexa or Google Assistant. Plus, with a 5-year warranty on all mechanical parts and labour, you can enjoy peace of mind knowing that your blinds are built to last.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"<b>Visit our showroom or book a free consultation today!</b>\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Sheer Horizon Blinds', 'Perfect Blinds for Every Window', 'Fast & Profe