\": \"uploads/z48qldfeghgloasome2d\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Eyelet Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749807774/uploads/rjni9pou60r5opxwey7c.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/rjni9pou60r5opxwey7c\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Eyelet Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749807776/uploads/gtm8i9br4lzv9gdclky2.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/gtm8i9br4lzv9gdclky2\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-07 09:16:28.308', '2025-12-02 05:40:52.177', '', 'High-quality, custom-made Eyelet curtains. We offer a variety of fabrics, linings, and styles for you to choose from.', 'Eyelet Curtains Dubai | Modern Designs with Free Installation', NULL, 'eyelet-curtains', 'Eyelet Curtains', '{"altText": "Eyelet Curtains", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747737406/uploads/o6ysqlzvuig1ypgzxigy.webp", "public_id": "uploads/o6ysqlzvuig1ypgzxigy", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Modern Eyelet Curtains for a Sleek<br>Look – Free Home Visit & Fast Installation!', 'Curtains that fit perfectly', '{}', '
', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Eyelet Curtains\", \"detail\": \"Eyelet curtains have metal rings punched directly into the fabric, so they glide smoothly on a curtain pole. It gives you a clean, modern aesthetic that feels natural and polished thanks to deep, even folds that hold their shape without constant adjustment. Since eyelet curtains don''t need tapes or hooks, they''re much easier to install and use, making them a practical choice for everyday use. For large windows, patio doors, and spaces that need to be constantly opened and closed, their design allows for fluid, uninterrupted movement. Because of their relaxed yet structured fall, they''re a favourite among those looking for a contemporary look without sacrificing comfort.\"}","{\"name\": \"Simple, Functional, and Beautiful in Every Light\", \"detail\": \"We offer a wide range of premium fabrics, including lightweight eyelet voile curtains for soft daylight diffusion, heavier velvets for a luxurious finish, and blackout eyelet curtain options for added darkness. With eyelet curtains, you don''t need additional fittings or tie-backs to maintain the shape, so they look well-balanced and tailored without extra effort.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"It''s all about customising, and we make sure every detail works for you. We guide you through the process, so your curtains not only look stunning but also function flawlessly. From choosing the right eyelet colour to match the pole you prefer to the perfect fabric weight and lining, the choices are endless.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"A good installation is just as important as a good curtain. Using our expert fitting team, your eyelet curtains are measured precisely, hung correctly, and spaced right for a flawless drape. When you move or update your space, we''ll happily reinstall your curtains so they look just as good as they did when you first got them. With free consultations, home measurements, and hassle-free installation, we make sure you get the most out of your curtains - not just now but for years to come.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Eyelet Curtains', 'Flawless function', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Book your free consultation today and experience the future of smart living', 'Handcrafted by artisans with a passion for creativity, Two Guys Home Furnishings help bring your imagination to reality with their best home decor services and products.', 'null', 4, 3, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
