", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Linen Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747740124/uploads/okbxmde5fyejtb4mqwxq.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/okbxmde5fyejtb4mqwxq\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Linen Curtains\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747740125/uploads/hijiij7c8xsejn2svjn0.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/hijiij7c8xsejn2svjn0\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-13 05:29:05.751', '2025-12-02 05:42:29.192', '', 'Custom-made linen curtains. Enjoy free installation, expert advice and free home visit for measurements.', 'Linen Curtains Dubai | Natural & Elegant Designs', NULL, 'linen-curtains', 'Linen Curtains', '{"altText": "Linen Curtains", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747740104/uploads/gmimzcrjmqwpfvnithhc.webp", "public_id": "uploads/gmimzcrjmqwpfvnithhc", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Timeless Linen Curtains, Custom-Made<br> – Free Home Visit & Wide Fabric Choices!', 'Custom curtains, classic charm', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Linen Curtains\", \"detail\": \"Linen’s beauty lies in its imperfections. It’s not meant to be rigid or overly structured. Instead, it has a soft, natural drape that makes a room feel inviting and effortless. Unlike polyester or cotton blends, pure linen curtains don''t hold onto sharp pleats or stiff folds—its beauty is in the way it moves. Whether you want a full, flowing curtain that pools slightly on the floor or a more tailored look that sits just right, linen adapts, never looking forced or artificial.\"}","{\"name\": \"Elegant drapes and Folds For Luxurious lifestyles\", \"detail\": \"At Two Guys Home Furnishings, we manufacture linen curtains in Dubai that are made to fit your space, not just your windows. Off-the-shelf linen curtains often fall short—too sheer, too short, or simply not weighted correctly to drape well. That’s why we take the time to measure, customise, and craft curtains that hang beautifully, move naturally, and suit your lifestyle. Whether you want airy, unlined linen that flows with the breeze or structured, lined linen for added privacy, we help you find the perfect balance.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"Installation matters just as much as the fabric. Linen window curtains need the right spacing, track, and length to hang properly and maintain their effortless look. Our expert team visit your home for free for measurements and installs them in 2 to 3 days, with the right height, width, and fullness to create the perfect drape. If you happen to move within 2 years, we offer free uninstallation and reinstallation at zero costs to you (if alterations are required, this is chargeable, but very nominal amounts)\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Linen Curtains', 'Flawless performance', 'Fast & Professional Service', 'Book your free consultation today and experience the future of smart living', 'Handcrafted by artisans with a passion for creativity, Two Guys Home Furnishings help bring your imagination to reality with their best home decor services and products.', 'null', 4, 3, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
