ds/ogmdraqcihsahhpninep.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/ogmdraqcihsahhpninep\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Tier on Tier Shutters\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1749809035/uploads/wf8t6yl5fc1a9v0becie.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/wf8t6yl5fc1a9v0becie\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}","{\"altText\": \"Tier on Tier Shutters\", \"imageUrl\": \"https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1764051660/uploads/cln0hv7t3wjbuopvcark.webp\", \"public_id\": \"uploads/cln0hv7t3wjbuopvcark\", \"resource_type\": \"image\"}"}', '2025-05-07 10:01:06.196', '2025-12-02 05:56:10.861', '', 'Discover custom Tier on Tier shutters in Dubai, a perfect balance of light and privacy. Choose MDF, Paulownia, or Basswood with expert fitting.

', 'Tier-on-Tier Shutters | Custom Design by Two Guys', NULL, 'tier-on-tier-shutters', 'Tier on Tier Shutters', '{"altText": "Tier on Tier Shutters", "imageUrl": "https://res.cloudinary.com/dsnhtfuef/image/upload/v1747810166/uploads/dv0spjygsl9m03sgcowb.webp", "public_id": "uploads/dv0spjygsl9m03sgcowb", "resource_type": "image"}', 'Tier on Tier Shutters – Perfect Balance of Light</br> and Privacy for Every Room in Dubai, UAE', 'Modern Shutters', '{}', '', '', '{"{\"name\": \"Tier-on-Tier Shutters\", \"detail\": \"Our Tier on Tier Shutters are designed with two separate shutter panels – one on top and one at the bottom, both of which allow you to control light and privacy independently. Keep the top open for natural light while keeping the bottom closed for privacy, or open both for a bright, airy feel. Whether it’s your living room, bedroom, or home office, these shutters bring a timeless look with modern practicality.\"}","{\"name\": \"\", \"detail\": \"At Two Guys, we design each Tier on Tier Shutter to your window’s exact measurements, ensuring a perfect fit and flawless finish. Crafted with accuracy and care.\"}","{\"name\": \"Crafted for Style and Strength – Choose the Material That Fits Your Space\", \"detail\": \"Our Tier on Tier Shutters are designed for flexibility. We offer three premium options – MDF, Paulownia, and Basswood – each crafted to suit your home’s style and needs. Our MDF material is perfect for living rooms, home offices, or hallways. They offer a smooth, modern finish at a great value. They’re durable, easy to clean, and maintain their look for years, making them ideal for spaces where you want an elegant design without the high maintenance.</br> Paulownia wood is the smart choice for larger windows, bay windows, or bright rooms where sunlight and airflow matter. Its lightweight strength makes it easy to operate the upper and lower panels, while the natural wood texture adds warmth and charm to any interior. For a premium touch, Basswood is perfect for bedrooms, lounges, or statement windows. It offers exceptional stability and a refined wood grain that complements both classic and modern interiors.  No matter which material you choose, our Tier on Tier Shutters are designed to fit your lifestyle beautifully.\"}"}', '{}', '', '{}', NULL, 'Tier on Tier Shutters', 'Elegant Control, Stylish Design', 'Fast & Professional Tier on Tier Shutter Service', 'Dubai’s Trusted Experts for Tier-on-Tier Shutters', 'Experience custom-crafted shutters that blend sophistication with functionality. At Two Guys, we provide free home consultations, accurate measurements, and expert installation, all backed by a 5-year warranty for lasting peace of mind and satisfaction.</br>Experience custom-crafted shutters that blend sophistication with functionality. At Two Guys, we provide free home consultations, accurate measurements, and expert installation, all backed by a 5-year warranty for lasting peace of mind and satisfaction.</br>Call us today at +971 50 597 4495 and let your windows make a statement with the perfect balance of light and privacy!', 'null', 4, 4, '', NULL, 'PUBLISHED');
